#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:1
msgid "YOLO Mode"
msgstr "YOLO 模式"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:3
msgid ""
"**YOLO mode** disables every safety gate ZeroClaw ships with. No approval "
"prompts, no workspace boundary, no shell policy, no command allow/denylist, "
"no OTP, no sandbox. The agent can run any shell command, touch any file, hit "
"any URL — immediately, without asking."
msgstr "**YOLO 模式**会禁用 ZeroClaw 提供的所有安全限制。没有审批提示、没有工作区边界、没有 shell 策略、没有命令允许/拒绝列表、没有 OTP、没有沙箱。代理可以立即运行任何 shell 命令、访问任何文件、请求任何 URL，无需询问。"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:5
msgid ""
"**This is for dev boxes, home labs, and throwaway VMs.** Do not run YOLO "
"mode on shared infrastructure. Do not run YOLO mode on a machine with "
"production credentials in its environment. Do not run YOLO mode if you do "
"not understand what an autonomous agent with `rm -rf` access can do."
msgstr "**此模式适用于开发机、家庭实验室以及临时虚拟机。** 请勿在共享基础设施上运行 YOLO 模式。请勿在环境变量中包含生产凭据的机器上运行 YOLO 模式。如果你不了解拥有 `rm -rf` 权限的自主代理能做什么，请勿运行 YOLO 模式。"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:7
msgid "When YOLO is the right call"
msgstr "当 YOLO 是最佳选择时"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:9
msgid ""
"A dev box where you're iterating fast and approval prompts slow you down"
msgstr "一个开发环境，你在其中快速迭代，而审批提示会拖慢你的进度"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:10
msgid "A throwaway container/VM used for agent experiments"
msgstr "用于代理实验的一次性容器/虚拟机"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:11
msgid "A home-lab SBC where you own every byte on the machine"
msgstr "一个家庭实验室的单板计算机（SBC），让你拥有机器上的每一个字节"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:12
msgid "CI/CD pipelines where the agent's actions are reviewed before merge"
msgstr "在合并之前审查代理操作的 CI/CD 流水线"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:14
msgid "When YOLO is the wrong call"
msgstr "当 YOLO 不是最佳选择时"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:16
msgid ""
"Your laptop with your email, your browser profile, and SSH keys to production"
msgstr "你的笔记本电脑中包含了你的电子邮件、浏览器配置文件以及用于生产环境的 SSH 密钥"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:17
msgid "A shared server"
msgstr "共享服务器"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:18
msgid "A VPS with live customers on it"
msgstr "一台有活跃客户的 VPS"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:19
msgid ""
"Anywhere the agent might be reached by an untrusted user through a channel — "
"a YOLO agent with a public Telegram bot is a Telegram-accessible root shell"
msgstr "在任何地方，如果代理可能通过某个渠道被不受信任的用户访问——例如，一个具有公共 Telegram 机器人的 YOLO 代理就是一个可通过 Telegram 访问的根 shell。"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:21
msgid "Enabling it"
msgstr "启用它"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:23
msgid "Add this to your config:"
msgstr "将此添加到您的配置中："

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:25
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[autonomy]\n"
"level = \"full\"\n"
"workspace_only = false\n"
"require_approval_for_medium_risk = false\n"
"block_high_risk_commands = false\n"
"allowed_commands = []\n"
"forbidden_paths = []\n"
"\n"
"[security.otp]\n"
"enabled = false\n"
"\n"
"[security.estop]\n"
"enabled = false\n"
"\n"
"[security.sandbox]\n"
"backend = \"noop\"\n"
"\n"
"[gateway]\n"
"pairing_required = false\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[autonomy]\nlevel = \"full\"\nworkspace_only = false\nrequire_approval_for_medium_risk = false\nblock_high_risk_commands = false\nallowed_commands = []\nforbidden_paths = []\n\n[security.otp]\nenabled = false\n\n[security.estop]\nenabled = false\n\n[security.sandbox]\nbackend = \"noop\"\n\n[gateway]\npairing_required = false\n```"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:47
msgid "Or — coming soon — a single preset:"
msgstr "或者——即将推出——一个预设："

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:49
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[autonomy]\n"
"mode = \"yolo\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[autonomy]\nmode = \"yolo\"\n```"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:54
msgid "which expands to the above at startup. Watch the release notes."
msgstr "在启动时展开为上述内容。请留意发行说明。"

#: src/getting-started/yolo.md:56
