"Examples: - `zeroclaw estop` - `zeroclaw estop --level network-kill` - "
"`zeroclaw estop --level domain-block --domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw "
"estop --level tool-freeze --tool shell --tool browser` - `zeroclaw estop "
"status` - `zeroclaw estop resume --network` - `zeroclaw estop resume --"
"domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop resume --tool shell`"
msgstr "示例：- `zeroclaw estop` - `zeroclaw estop --level network-kill` - `zeroclaw estop --level domain-block --domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop --level tool-freeze --tool shell --tool browser` - `zeroclaw estop status` - `zeroclaw estop resume --network` - `zeroclaw estop resume --domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop resume --tool shell`"

