msgstr "`--otp <OTP>` — OTP 验证码。如果省略且需要 OTP，则会显示提示"

#: src/reference/cli.md:508
msgid "`zeroclaw cron`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:510
msgid "Configure and manage scheduled tasks."
msgstr "配置和管理定时任务。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:512
msgid ""
"Schedule recurring, one-shot, or interval-based tasks using cron "
"expressions, RFC 3339 timestamps, durations, or fixed intervals."
msgstr "使用 cron 表达式、RFC 3339 时间戳、持续时间或固定间隔来安排周期性、一次性或基于间隔的任务。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:514
msgid ""
"Cron expressions use the standard 5-field format: 'min hour day month "
"weekday'. Timezones default to UTC; override with --tz and an IANA timezone "
"name."
msgstr "Cron 表达式使用标准的 5 字段格式：'min hour day month weekday'。时区默认为 UTC；可通过 --tz 和 IANA 时区名称进行覆盖。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:516
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron list zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' "
"--tz America/New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check "
"system health' --agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok' zeroclaw "
"cron add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z 'Send reminder' --agent zeroclaw cron add-"
"every 60000 'Ping heartbeat' zeroclaw cron once 30m 'Run backup in 30 "
"minutes' --agent zeroclaw cron pause TASK_ID zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --"
"expression '0 8 * * \\*' --tz Europe/London"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw cron list zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' '早上好' --tz America/New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' '检查系统健康状态' --agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok' zeroclaw cron add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z '发送提醒' --agent zeroclaw cron add-every 60000 'Ping 心跳' zeroclaw cron once 30m '30 分钟后运行备份' --agent zeroclaw cron pause TASK_ID zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --expression '0 8 * * \\*' --tz Europe/London"

#: src/reference/cli.md:527
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw cron <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:531
msgid "`list` — List all scheduled tasks"
msgstr "`list` — 列出所有计划任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:532
msgid "`add` — Add a new scheduled task"
msgstr "`add` — 添加新的计划任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:533
msgid "`add-at` — Add a one-shot scheduled task at an RFC3339 timestamp"
msgstr "`add-at` — 在 RFC3339 时间戳处添加一个一次性定时任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:534
msgid "`add-every` — Add a fixed-interval scheduled task"
msgstr "`add-every` — 添加一个固定间隔的定时任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:535
msgid "`once` — Add a one-shot delayed task (e.g. \"30m\", \"2h\", \"1d\")"
msgstr "`once` — 添加一个一次性延迟任务（例如 \"30m\"、\"2h\"、\"1d\"）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:536
msgid "`remove` — Remove a scheduled task"
msgstr "`remove` — 移除已调度的任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:537
msgid "`update` — Update a scheduled task"
msgstr "`update` — 更新计划任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:538
msgid "`pause` — Pause a scheduled task"
msgstr "`pause` — 暂停计划任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:539
msgid "`resume` — Resume a paused task"
msgstr "`resume` — 恢复暂停的任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:543
msgid "`zeroclaw cron list`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:545
msgid "List all scheduled tasks"
msgstr "列出所有计划任务"

#: src/reference/cli.md:547
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron list`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw cron list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:551
msgid "`zeroclaw cron add`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron add`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:553
msgid "Add a new recurring scheduled task."
msgstr "添加一个新的周期性计划任务。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:555
msgid ""
"Uses standard 5-field cron syntax: 'min hour day month weekday'. Times are "
"evaluated in UTC by default; use --tz with an IANA timezone name to override."
msgstr "使用标准的 5 字段 cron 语法：'min hour day month weekday'。默认情况下，时间以 UTC 进行评估；使用 --tz 和 IANA 时区名称来覆盖。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:557
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' --tz America/"
"New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check system health' --"
"agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok'"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' --tz America/New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check system health' --agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:562
