msgstr "示例：zeroclaw cron once 30m '在 30 分钟后运行备份' zeroclaw cron once 2h '跟进部署' zeroclaw cron once 1d '每日检查'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:636
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron once [OPTIONS] <DELAY> <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw cron once [OPTIONS] <DELAY> <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:640
