"Examples: zeroclaw hardware discover zeroclaw hardware introspect /dev/"
"ttyACM0 zeroclaw hardware info --chip STM32F401RETx"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw 硬件发现 zeroclaw 硬件内省 /dev/ttyACM0 zeroclaw 硬件信息 --chip STM32F401RETx"

