"Scans connected USB devices by VID/PID and matches them against known "
"development boards (STM32 Nucleo, Arduino, ESP32)."
msgstr "通过 VID/PID 扫描已连接的 USB 设备，并将其与已知的开发板（STM32 Nucleo、Arduino、ESP32）进行匹配。"

