"`flash-nucleo` — Flash ZeroClaw firmware to Nucleo-F401RE (builds + probe-rs "
"run)"
msgstr "`flash-nucleo` — 将 ZeroClaw 固件烧录到 Nucleo-F401RE（构建 + probe-rs 运行）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1320
msgid "`zeroclaw peripheral list`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 外围设备列表`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1322
msgid "List configured peripherals"
msgstr "列出已配置的外设"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1324
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw peripheral list`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw peripheral list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1328
msgid "`zeroclaw peripheral add`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw peripheral add`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1330
msgid "Add a peripheral by board type and transport path."
msgstr "按主板类型和传输路径添加外围设备。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1332
msgid ""
"Registers a hardware board so the agent can use its tools (GPIO, sensors, "
"actuators). Use 'native' as path for local GPIO on single-board computers "
"like Raspberry Pi."
msgstr "注册硬件板，以便代理可以使用其工具（GPIO、传感器、执行器）。在树莓派等单板计算机上，使用“native”作为本地 GPIO 的路径。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1334
msgid "Supported boards: nucleo-f401re, rpi-gpio, esp32, arduino-uno."
msgstr "支持的板子：nucleo-f401re、rpi-gpio、esp32、arduino-uno。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1336
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw peripheral add nucleo-f401re /dev/ttyACM0 zeroclaw "
"peripheral add rpi-gpio native zeroclaw peripheral add esp32 /dev/ttyUSB0"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw peripheral add nucleo-f401re /dev/ttyACM0 zeroclaw peripheral add rpi-gpio native zeroclaw peripheral add esp32 /dev/ttyUSB0"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1341
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw peripheral add <BOARD> <PATH>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw peripheral add <BOARD> <PATH>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1345
msgid "`<BOARD>` — Board type (nucleo-f401re, rpi-gpio, esp32)"
msgstr "`<BOARD>` — 开发板类型（nucleo-f401re、rpi-gpio、esp32）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1346
msgid ""
"`<PATH>` — Path for serial transport (/dev/ttyACM0) or \"native\" for local "
"GPIO"
msgstr "`<PATH>` — 串行传输的路径（例如 /dev/ttyACM0）或用于本地 GPIO 的 \"native\""

#: src/reference/cli.md:1350
msgid "`zeroclaw peripheral flash`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 外围闪存`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1352
msgid "Flash ZeroClaw firmware to an Arduino board."
msgstr "将 Flash ZeroClaw 固件刷写到 Arduino 开发板上。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1354
msgid ""
"Generates the .ino sketch, installs arduino-cli if it is not already "
"available, compiles, and uploads the firmware."
msgstr "生成 .ino 草图，如果尚未安装则安装 arduino-cli，编译并上传固件。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1356
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw peripheral flash zeroclaw peripheral flash --port /dev/cu."
"usbmodem12345 zeroclaw peripheral flash -p COM3"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw 外围设备闪存 zeroclaw 外围设备闪存 --port /dev/cu.usbmodem12345 zeroclaw 外围设备闪存 -p COM3"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1361
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw peripheral flash [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw peripheral flash [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1365
msgid ""
"`-p`, `--port <PORT>` — Serial port (e.g. /dev/cu.usbmodem12345). If "
"omitted, uses first arduino-uno from config"
msgstr "`-p`, `--port <PORT>` — 串口（例如 /dev/cu.usbmodem12345）。如果省略，则使用配置中的第一个 arduino-uno"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1369
msgid "`zeroclaw peripheral setup-uno-q`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 外围设备 setup-uno-q`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1371
msgid "Setup Arduino Uno Q Bridge app (deploy GPIO bridge for agent control)"
msgstr "设置 Arduino Uno Q Bridge 应用（部署 GPIO 桥接器以进行代理控制）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1373
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw peripheral setup-uno-q [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw peripheral setup-uno-q [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1377
msgid ""
"`--host <HOST>` — Uno Q IP (e.g. 192.168.0.48). If omitted, assumes running "
"ON the Uno Q"
msgstr "`--host <HOST>` — Uno Q 的 IP 地址（例如 192.168.0.48）。如果省略此参数，则假定运行在 Uno Q 上。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1381 src/hardware/nucleo-setup.md:38
#: src/hardware/nucleo-setup.md:116
msgid "`zeroclaw peripheral flash-nucleo`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 外围设备 flash-nucleo`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1383
msgid "Flash ZeroClaw firmware to Nucleo-F401RE (builds + probe-rs run)"
msgstr "将 ZeroClaw 固件刷写到 Nucleo-F401RE（构建 + probe-rs 运行）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1385
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw peripheral flash-nucleo`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw peripheral flash-nucleo`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1389
msgid "`zeroclaw memory`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw memory`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1391
msgid "Manage agent memory entries."
msgstr "管理代理内存条目。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1393
msgid ""
"List, inspect, and clear memory entries stored by the agent. Supports "
"filtering by category and session, pagination, and batch clearing with "
"confirmation."
msgstr "列出、检查并清除代理存储的内存条目。支持按类别和会话进行过滤、分页以及带确认的批量清除。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1395
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw memory stats zeroclaw memory list zeroclaw memory list --"
"category core --limit 10 zeroclaw memory get KEY zeroclaw memory clear --"
"category conversation --yes"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw 内存统计 zeroclaw 内存列表 zeroclaw 内存列表 --category core --limit 10 zeroclaw 内存获取 KEY zeroclaw 内存清除 --category conversation --yes"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1402
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw memory <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw memory <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1406
msgid "`list` — List memory entries with optional filters"
msgstr "`list` — 列出内存条目，支持可选的过滤条件"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1407
msgid "`get` — Get a specific memory entry by key"
msgstr "`get` — 根据键获取特定的内存条目"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1408
msgid "`stats` — Show memory backend statistics and health"
msgstr "`stats` — 显示内存后端统计信息和健康状况"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1409
msgid "`clear` — Clear memories by category, by key, or clear all"
msgstr "`clear` — 按类别、按键清除记忆，或清除所有记忆"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1413
msgid "`zeroclaw memory list`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw memory list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1415
msgid "List memory entries with optional filters"
msgstr "列出内存条目，并可选地应用过滤器"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1417
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw memory list [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw memory list [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1421 src/reference/cli.md:1461
msgid "`--category <CATEGORY>`"
msgstr "`--category <CATEGORY>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1422
msgid "`--session <SESSION>`"
msgstr "`--session <SESSION>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1423
msgid "`--limit <LIMIT>`"
msgstr "`--limit <LIMIT>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1426
msgid "`--offset <OFFSET>`"
msgstr "`--offset <OFFSET>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1428
msgid "Default value: `0`"
msgstr "默认值：`0`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1432
msgid "`zeroclaw memory get`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw memory get`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1434
msgid "Get a specific memory entry by key"
msgstr "通过键获取特定的内存条目"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1436
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw memory get <KEY>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw memory get <KEY>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1440
msgid "`<KEY>`"
msgstr "`<KEY>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1444
msgid "`zeroclaw memory stats`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 内存统计`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1446
msgid "Show memory backend statistics and health"
msgstr "显示内存后端统计信息和健康状况"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1448
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw memory stats`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw memory stats`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1452
msgid "`zeroclaw memory clear`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw memory clear`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1454
msgid "Clear memories by category, by key, or clear all"
msgstr "按类别、按键清除记忆，或清除所有记忆"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1456
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw memory clear [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw memory clear [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1460
msgid "`--key <KEY>` — Delete a single entry by key (supports prefix match)"
msgstr "`--key <KEY>` — 按键删除单个条目（支持前缀匹配）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1462
msgid "`--yes` — Skip confirmation prompt"
msgstr "`--yes` — 跳过确认提示"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1466
msgid "`zeroclaw config`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1468
msgid "Manage ZeroClaw configuration."
msgstr "管理 ZeroClaw 配置。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1470
msgid ""
"View, set, or initialize config properties by dotted path. Use 'schema' to "
"dump the full JSON Schema for the config file."
msgstr "通过点分路径查看、设置或初始化配置属性。使用 'schema' 可导出配置文件完整的 JSON Schema。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1472
msgid ""
"Properties are addressed by dotted path (e.g. channels.matrix.mention-only). "
"Secret fields (API keys, tokens) automatically use masked input. Enum fields "
"offer interactive selection when value is omitted."
msgstr "属性通过点分路径进行寻址（例如 channels.matrix.mention-only）。密钥字段（如 API 密钥、令牌）会自动使用掩码输入。当值省略时，枚举字段提供交互式选择。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1476
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw config list                                  # list all "
"properties zeroclaw config list --secrets                        # list only "
"secrets zeroclaw config list --filter channels.matrix         # filter by "
"prefix zeroclaw config get channels.matrix.mention-only      # get a value "
"zeroclaw config set channels.matrix.mention-only true # set a value zeroclaw "
"config set channels.matrix.access-token      # secret: masked input zeroclaw "
"config set channels.matrix.stream-mode       # enum: interactive select "
"zeroclaw config init channels.matrix                  # init section with "
"defaults zeroclaw config schema                                # print JSON "
"Schema to stdout zeroclaw config schema > schema.json"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw config list                                  # 列出所有属性 zeroclaw config list --secrets                        # 仅列出密钥 zeroclaw config list --filter channels.matrix         # 按前缀过滤 zeroclaw config get channels.matrix.mention-only      # 获取一个值 zeroclaw config set channels.matrix.mention-only true # 设置一个值 zeroclaw config set channels.matrix.access-token      # 密钥：掩码输入 zeroclaw config set channels.matrix.stream-mode       # 枚举：交互式选择 zeroclaw config init channels.matrix                  # 使用默认值初始化部分 zeroclaw config schema                                # 将 JSON Schema 打印到标准输出 zeroclaw config schema > schema.json"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1488
msgid ""
"Property path tab completion is included automatically in `zeroclaw "
"completions <shell>`."
msgstr "属性路径的 Tab 补全功能已自动包含在 `zeroclaw completions <shell>` 中。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1490
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1494
msgid "`schema` — Dump the full configuration JSON Schema to stdout"
msgstr "`schema` — 将完整的配置 JSON Schema 转储到标准输出"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1495
msgid "`list` — List all config properties with current values"
msgstr "`list` — 列出所有配置属性及其当前值"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1496
msgid "`get` — Get a config property value"
msgstr "`get` — 获取配置属性值"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1497
msgid ""
"`set` — Set a config property (secret fields auto-prompt for masked input)"
msgstr "`set` — 设置配置属性（敏感字段会自动提示以掩码方式输入）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1498
msgid "`init` — Initialize unconfigured sections with defaults (enabled=false)"
msgstr "`init` — 使用默认值（enabled=false）初始化未配置的部分"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1499
msgid ""
"`migrate` — Migrate config.toml to the current schema version on disk "
"(preserves comments)"
msgstr "`migrate` — 将 config.toml 迁移到磁盘上的当前 schema 版本（保留注释）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1503
msgid "`zeroclaw config schema`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config schema`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1505
msgid "Dump the full configuration JSON Schema to stdout"
msgstr "将完整的配置 JSON Schema 转储到标准输出"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1507
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config schema`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config schema`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1511
msgid "`zeroclaw config list`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1513
msgid "List all config properties with current values"
msgstr "列出所有配置属性及其当前值"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1515
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config list [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config list [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1519
msgid ""
"`-f`, `--filter <FILTER>` — Filter by path prefix (e.g. \"channels.telegram"
"\")"
msgstr "`-f`, `--filter <FILTER>` — 按路径前缀进行过滤（例如 \"channels.telegram\"）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1520
msgid "`--secrets` — Show only secret (encrypted) fields"
msgstr "`--secrets` — 仅显示机密（加密）字段"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1524
msgid "`zeroclaw config get`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config get`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1526
msgid "Get a config property value"
msgstr "获取配置属性值"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1528
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config get <PATH>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config get <PATH>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1532
msgid "`<PATH>` — Property path (e.g. channels.telegram.mention-only)"
msgstr "`<PATH>` — 属性路径（例如 channels.telegram.mention-only）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1536
msgid "`zeroclaw config set`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config set`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1538
msgid "Set a config property (secret fields auto-prompt for masked input)"
msgstr "设置配置属性（秘密字段自动提示以进行掩码输入）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1540
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config set [OPTIONS] <PATH> [VALUE]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config set [OPTIONS] <PATH> [VALUE]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1544
msgid "`<PATH>` — Property path"
msgstr "`<PATH>` — 属性路径"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1545
msgid "`<VALUE>` — New value (omit for secret fields to get masked input)"
msgstr "`<VALUE>` — 新值（对于密钥字段，省略此参数以获取掩码输入）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1549
msgid ""
"`--no-interactive` — Skip interactive prompts — require value on command "
"line, accept raw strings for enums"
msgstr "`--no-interactive` — 跳过交互式提示 — 要求在命令行上提供值，接受枚举的原始字符串"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1553
msgid "`zeroclaw config init`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config init`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1555
msgid "Initialize unconfigured sections with defaults (enabled=false)"
msgstr "使用默认值（enabled=false）初始化未配置的节"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1557
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config init [SECTION]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config init [SECTION]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1561
msgid "`<SECTION>` — Section prefix (e.g. channels.matrix). Omit to init all"
msgstr "`<SECTION>` — 节前缀（例如 channels.matrix）。省略则初始化所有"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1565
msgid "`zeroclaw config migrate`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw config migrate`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1567
msgid ""
"Migrate config.toml to the current schema version on disk (preserves "
"comments)"
msgstr "将 config.toml 迁移到磁盘上的当前架构版本（保留注释）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1569
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw config migrate`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw config migrate`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1573
msgid "`zeroclaw update`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw update`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1575
msgid "Check for and apply ZeroClaw updates."
msgstr "检查并应用 ZeroClaw 更新。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1577
msgid ""
"By default, downloads and installs the latest release with a 6-phase "
"pipeline: preflight, download, backup, validate, swap, and smoke test. "
"Automatic rollback on failure."
msgstr "默认情况下，下载并安装最新版本，采用 6 阶段流水线：预检、下载、备份、验证、切换和冒烟测试。失败时自动回滚。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1579
msgid ""
"Use --check to only check for updates without installing. Use --force to "
"skip the confirmation prompt. Use --version to target a specific release "
"instead of latest."
msgstr "使用 `--check` 仅检查更新而不安装。使用 `--force` 跳过确认提示。使用 `--version` 指定目标版本，而非最新版本。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1583
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw update                      # download and install latest "
"zeroclaw update --check              # check only, don't install zeroclaw "
"update --force              # install without confirmation zeroclaw update --"
"version 0.6.0      # install specific version"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw update                      # 下载并安装最新的 zeroclaw 更新 --check              # 仅检查，不安装 zeroclaw update --force              # 无需确认即安装 zeroclaw update --version 0.6.0      # 安装指定版本"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1589
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw update [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw update [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1593
msgid "`--check` — Only check for updates, don't install"
msgstr "`--check` — 仅检查更新，不安装"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1594
msgid "`--force` — Skip confirmation prompt"
msgstr "`--force` — 跳过确认提示"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1595
msgid "`--version <VERSION>` — Target version (default: latest)"
msgstr "`--version <VERSION>` — 目标版本（默认：最新版本）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1599
msgid "`zeroclaw self-test`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 自检`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1601
msgid "Run diagnostic self-tests to verify the ZeroClaw installation."
msgstr "运行诊断自检以验证 ZeroClaw 的安装。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1603
msgid ""
"By default, runs the full test suite including network checks (gateway "
"health, memory round-trip). Use --quick to skip network checks for faster "
"offline validation."
msgstr "默认情况下，运行完整的测试套件，包括网络检查（网关健康检查、内存往返测试）。使用 `--quick` 可跳过网络检查，以进行更快的离线验证。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1605
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw self-test             # full suite zeroclaw self-test --"
"quick     # quick checks only (no network)"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw self-test             # 完整套件 zeroclaw self-test --quick     # 仅快速检查（无网络）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1609
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw self-test [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw self-test [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1613
msgid "`--quick` — Run quick checks only (no network)"
msgstr "`--quick` — 仅运行快速检查（无需网络）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1617
msgid "`zeroclaw completions`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 补全`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1619
msgid "Generate shell completion scripts for `zeroclaw`."
msgstr "为 `zeroclaw` 生成 shell 补全脚本。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1621
msgid "The script is printed to stdout so it can be sourced directly:"
msgstr "该脚本会输出到标准输出（stdout），以便可以直接通过 `source` 命令加载："

#: src/reference/cli.md:1623
msgid ""
"Examples: source \\<(zeroclaw completions bash) zeroclaw completions zsh > "
"~/.zfunc/\\_zeroclaw zeroclaw completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/"
"zeroclaw.fish"
msgstr "示例：source \\<(zeroclaw completions bash) zeroclaw completions zsh > ~/.zfunc/\\_zeroclaw zeroclaw completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/zeroclaw.fish"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1628
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw completions <SHELL>`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw completions <SHELL>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1632
msgid "`<SHELL>` — Target shell"
msgstr "`<SHELL>` — 目标 Shell"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1634
msgid "Possible values: `bash`, `fish`, `zsh`, `powershell`, `elvish`"
msgstr "可能的值：`bash`、`fish`、`zsh`、`powershell`、`elvish`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1639
msgid "`zeroclaw desktop`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw 桌面版`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1641
msgid "Launch the ZeroClaw companion desktop app."
msgstr "启动 ZeroClaw 伴侣桌面应用。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1643
msgid ""
"The companion app is a lightweight menu bar / system tray application that "
"connects to the same gateway as the CLI. It provides quick access to the "
"dashboard, status monitoring, and device pairing."
msgstr "配套应用是一个轻量级的菜单栏/系统托盘应用程序，它与 CLI 连接到同一个网关。它提供对仪表板、状态监控和设备配对的快速访问。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1645
msgid ""
"Use --install to download the pre-built companion app for your platform."
msgstr "使用 --install 下载适用于您平台的预构建的配套应用。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1647
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw desktop              # launch the companion app zeroclaw "
"desktop --install    # download and install it"
msgstr "示例：zeroclaw desktop              # 启动配套应用 zeroclaw desktop --install    # 下载并安装它"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1651
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw desktop [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**用法：** `zeroclaw desktop [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:1655
msgid "`--install` — Download and install the companion app"
msgstr "`--install` — 下载并安装配套应用"

