"Every model provider is declared under `[providers.models.<name>]` in `~/."
"zeroclaw/config.toml`. The `<name>` is your own alias — it's how you "
"reference the provider elsewhere in config (`default_model = \"claude\"`, "
"`fallback_providers = [\"claude\", \"local\"]`, etc.)."
msgstr "每个模型提供商都在 `~/.zeroclaw/config.toml` 中的 `[providers.models.<name>]` 下声明。`<name>` 是你自定义的别名——它用于在配置的其他部分引用该提供商（例如 `default_model = \"claude\"`、`fallback_providers = [\"claude\", \"local\"]` 等）。"

