msgid ""
"Every provider ZeroClaw ships with. For each: what it talks to, config "
"shape, and notes."
msgstr "ZeroClaw 自带的每个提供程序。对于每个提供程序：它通信的对象、配置结构以及注意事项。"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:5
msgid "See [Configuration](./configuration.md) for universal fields."
msgstr "有关通用字段，请参阅 [配置](./configuration.md)。"

