"[providers.models.claude]\n"
"kind = \"anthropic\"\n"
"model = \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\"     # or claude-sonnet-4-6, claude-"
"opus-4-7\n"
"api_key = \"sk-ant-...\"                   # or \"sk-ant-oat-...\" for "
"OAuth\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[providers.models.claude]\nkind = \"anthropic\"\nmodel = \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\"     # 或 claude-sonnet-4-6、claude-opus-4-7\napi_key = \"sk-ant-...\"                   # 或使用 OAuth 时填写 \"sk-ant-oat-...\"\n```"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:20
msgid ""
"Supports OAuth tokens (`sk-ant-oat*`) from Claude Pro/Team subscriptions — "
"no separate API billing. Streaming, tool calls, vision, and reasoning all "
"supported."
msgstr "支持来自 Claude Pro/Team 订阅的 OAuth 令牌（`sk-ant-oat*`）——无需单独的 API 计费。支持流式传输、工具调用、视觉和推理功能。"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:22
msgid "OpenAI"
msgstr "OpenAI"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:24
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[providers.models.gpt]\n"
"kind = \"openai\"\n"
"model = \"gpt-4o-mini\"\n"
"api_key = \"sk-...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[providers.models.gpt]\nkind = \"openai\"\nmodel = \"gpt-4o-mini\"\napi_key = \"sk-...\"\n```"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:31
msgid ""
"GPT-4o, GPT-5, o-series reasoning models. Reasoning tokens surfaced as "
"`ReasoningDelta` events; see [Streaming](./streaming.md)."
msgstr "GPT-4o、GPT-5、o 系列推理模型。推理令牌以 `ReasoningDelta` 事件形式呈现；详见 [流式传输](./streaming.md)。"

#: src/providers/catalog.md:35
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
