msgstr "[配置参考](../reference/config.md) — 完整的配置字段索引"

#: src/channels/line.md:146
msgid ""
"[LINE Developers Documentation](https://developers.line.biz/en/docs/"
"messaging-api/)"
msgstr "[LINE 开发者文档](https://developers.line.biz/en/docs/messaging-api/)"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:3
msgid ""
"Nextcloud Talk integration via the Talk Bot webhook protocol. Self-hosted, "
"federated, and E2E-capable — another sovereign-communication option "
"alongside [Matrix](./matrix.md) and [Mattermost](./mattermost.md)."
msgstr "通过 Talk Bot Webhook 协议集成 Nextcloud Talk。支持自托管、联邦化以及端到端加密——与 [Matrix](./matrix.md) 和 [Mattermost](./mattermost.md) 并列的另一种自主通信选项。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:5
msgid "What this integration does"
msgstr "此集成实现的功能"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:7
msgid "Receives inbound Talk events via `POST /nextcloud-talk` on the gateway"
msgstr "通过网关接收来自 `POST /nextcloud-talk` 的入站 Talk 事件"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:8
msgid "Verifies webhook signatures (HMAC-SHA256) when a secret is configured"
msgstr "在配置了密钥时，验证 Webhook 签名（HMAC-SHA256）"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:9
msgid "Sends replies back to Talk rooms via the Nextcloud OCS API"
msgstr "通过 Nextcloud OCS API 将回复发送回 Talk 房间"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:13
msgid ""
"**Nextcloud server** with the Talk app enabled (v17 or later recommended)"
msgstr "**Nextcloud 服务器**，已启用 Talk 应用（建议使用 v17 或更高版本）"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:14
msgid ""
"**Bot account** in Talk settings — give it a display name (e.g. `zeroclaw-"
"bot`) and generate a bot webhook URL"
msgstr "**机器人账号** 在“聊天设置”中 — 为其指定一个显示名称（例如 `zeroclaw-bot`）并生成一个机器人 Webhook URL"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:15
msgid ""
"**Webhook secret** from the Talk admin UI if you want signature verification "
"(strongly recommended)"
msgstr "来自 Talk 管理界面的 **Webhook 密钥**，如果你希望进行签名验证（强烈建议）。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:16
msgid ""
"**Publicly-reachable gateway** — see [Setup → Container](../setup/container."
"md) for tunnel options if self-hosted"
msgstr "**可公开访问的网关** — 如果是自托管，请参阅 [设置 → 容器](../setup/container.md) 以获取隧道选项"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:20
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.nextcloud_talk]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"server_url = \"https://cloud.example.com\"\n"
"bot_name = \"zeroclaw-bot\"                      # the display name of the "
"bot in Talk\n"
"webhook_secret = \"...\"                         # shared secret from Talk "
"admin UI\n"
"username = \"...\"                               # bot's Nextcloud login for "
"outbound API\n"
"password = \"...\"                               # app password (not the "
"account password)\n"
"allowed_rooms = [\"ROOM-TOKEN-1\"]               # tokens from webhook "
"payloads\n"
"allowed_users = [\"*\"]                          # actor IDs; \"*\" = allow "
"all (use for first-time test only)\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.nextcloud_talk]\nenabled = true\nserver_url = \"https://cloud.example.com\"\nbot_name = \"zeroclaw-bot\"                      # 机器人（Bot）在 Talk 中的显示名称\nwebhook_secret = \"...\"                         # 来自 Talk 管理界面的共享密钥\nusername = \"...\"                               # 机器人（Bot）用于出站 API 的 Nextcloud 登录名\npassword = \"...\"                               # 应用密码（非账户密码）\nallowed_rooms = [\"ROOM-TOKEN-1\"]               # 来自 webhook 负载的令牌\nallowed_users = [\"*\"]                          # 参与者 ID；\"*\" = 允许所有（仅用于首次测试）\n```"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:32
msgid ""
"Environment override: `ZEROCLAW_NEXTCLOUD_TALK_WEBHOOK_SECRET` takes "
"precedence over the config value. Useful for rotating secrets without "
"editing the config."
msgstr "环境变量覆盖：`ZEROCLAW_NEXTCLOUD_TALK_WEBHOOK_SECRET` 的优先级高于配置文件中的值。适用于在不修改配置文件的情况下轮换密钥。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:34
msgid "Full field reference: [Config](../reference/config.md)."
msgstr "完整字段参考：[Config](../reference/config.md)。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:36
msgid "Gateway endpoint"
msgstr "网关端点"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:42
msgid "Configure your Talk bot's webhook URL to point at:"
msgstr "将您的 Talk 机器人的 Webhook URL 配置为指向："

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:44
msgid ""
"```\n"
"https://<your-public-url>/nextcloud-talk\n"
"```"
msgstr "```\nhttps://<your-public-url>/nextcloud-talk\n```"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:48
msgid ""
"Local development? Configure `[tunnel]` in your config (ngrok, Cloudflare, "
"or Tailscale) and the gateway exposes itself on startup — see [Operations → "
"Network deployment](../ops/network-deployment.md)."
msgstr "本地开发？在配置文件中配置 `[tunnel]`（ngrok、Cloudflare 或 Tailscale），网关将在启动时自动暴露自身——参见 [操作 → 网络部署](../ops/network-deployment.md)。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:50 src/channels/webhook.md:29
msgid "Signature verification"
msgstr "签名验证"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:52
msgid "When `webhook_secret` is set, inbound requests must carry:"
msgstr "当设置了 `webhook_secret` 时，传入的请求必须携带："

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:54
msgid "`X-Nextcloud-Talk-Random` header"
msgstr "`X-Nextcloud-Talk-Random` 头"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:55
msgid "`X-Nextcloud-Talk-Signature` header"
msgstr "`X-Nextcloud-Talk-Signature` 头"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:57
msgid "ZeroClaw verifies:"
msgstr "ZeroClaw 验证："

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:65
msgid ""
"Without a secret, no verification — don't expose this endpoint publicly in "
"that mode."
msgstr "没有密钥就无法进行验证——在该模式下不要公开暴露此端点。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:67
msgid "Message routing"
msgstr "消息路由"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:69
msgid ""
"**Bot-originated events** (`actorType = \"bots\"`) are ignored — prevents "
"feedback loops"
msgstr "**由机器人发起的事件**（`actorType = \"bots\"`）将被忽略——以防止反馈循环"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:70
msgid "**System events** (joins, leaves, membership changes) are ignored"
msgstr "**系统事件**（加入、离开、成员资格变更）将被忽略"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:71
msgid "**Non-message events** are ignored"
msgstr "**非消息事件**将被忽略"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:72
msgid "**User messages** are dispatched to the agent loop"
msgstr "**用户消息**会被分发到代理循环中"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:73
msgid ""
"**Replies** go back to the originating room via the `token` in the webhook "
"payload"
msgstr "**回复**会通过 webhook 负载中的 `token` 返回到原始房间"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:75
msgid "Quick validation"
msgstr "快速验证"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:77
msgid "Set `allowed_users = [\"*\"]` for first-time testing"
msgstr "首次测试时，设置 `allowed_users = [\"*\"]`"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:78
msgid "Send a test message in the configured Talk room"
msgstr "在配置的 Talk 房间中发送一条测试消息"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:79
msgid "Confirm ZeroClaw receives and replies in the same room"
msgstr "确认 ZeroClaw 在同一个房间中接收和回复"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:80
msgid ""
"Tighten `allowed_users` to explicit actor IDs (e.g. `[\"alice\", \"bob\"]`)"
msgstr "将 `allowed_users` 收紧为明确的参与者 ID（例如 `[\"alice\", \"bob\"]`）"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:84
msgid ""
"**`404 Nextcloud Talk not configured`** — `[channels.nextcloud_talk]` "
"section missing or `enabled = false`"
msgstr "**`404 Nextcloud Talk 未配置`** — `[channels.nextcloud_talk]` 部分缺失或 `enabled = false`"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:85
msgid ""
"**`401 Invalid signature`** — secret mismatch, wrong random header, or body-"
"signing bug. Check the raw body is being signed (not the parsed JSON)"
msgstr "**`401 签名无效`** — 密钥不匹配、随机标头错误，或主体签名存在 bug。请检查是否对原始主体进行了签名（而非已解析的 JSON）。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:86
msgid ""
"**No reply, webhook `200`** — event was filtered. Check logs for \"actorType "
"= bots\" or \"user not in allowed_users\""
msgstr "**无回复，webhook `200`** — 事件已被过滤。请检查日志中的 \"actorType = bots\" 或 \"user not in allowed_users\""

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:87
msgid ""
"**Replies delivered but look wrong** — check thread context; Talk replies "
"are currently root-level only"
msgstr "**已发送回复，但显示不正确** — 请检查线程上下文；目前 Talk 回复仅支持根级别"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:91
msgid ""
"Nextcloud Talk does not support message edits via the Bot API, so streaming "
"draft updates are disabled for this channel. Replies are sent on stream "
"completion only."
msgstr "Nextcloud Talk 不支持通过 Bot API 编辑消息，因此该通道的流式草稿更新已禁用。回复仅在流完成时发送。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:95
msgid ""
"TLS: terminate at your reverse proxy; webhook signature verification works "
"over HTTP-to-container loopback"
msgstr "TLS：在反向代理处终止；Webhook 签名验证通过 HTTP 到容器回环连接工作"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:96
msgid ""
"The OCS API is authenticated via HTTP Basic — use an app password, not the "
"account password"
msgstr "OCS API 通过 HTTP Basic 进行身份验证——请使用应用密码，而不是账户密码"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:97
msgid ""
"Rate limits are Nextcloud-server dependent; the default bot doesn't run into "
"them in normal conversation cadences"
msgstr "速率限制取决于 Nextcloud-server；默认机器人不会在正常的对话频率中遇到这些限制。"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:101
msgid "[Matrix](./matrix.md) — richer E2EE but more operational complexity"
msgstr "[Matrix](./matrix.md) — 更丰富的端到端加密（E2EE），但操作复杂性更高"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:102
msgid ""
"[Mattermost](./mattermost.md) — similar self-hosted posture, different "
"protocol"
msgstr "[Mattermost](./mattermost.md) — 类似的自托管架构，但使用不同的协议"

#: src/channels/nextcloud-talk.md:103 src/channels/acp.md:121
msgid "[Channels → Overview](./overview.md)"
msgstr "[通道 → 概述](./overview.md)"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:1
msgid "Other Chat Platforms"
msgstr "其他聊天平台"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:3
msgid ""
"Channels with working integrations but not yet pulled out into dedicated "
"guides. Each is feature-gated; enable the matching `channel-<name>` feature "
"at build time."
msgstr "具有可用集成但尚未提取为独立指南的通道。每个通道都通过功能门控进行控制；在构建时启用相应的 `channel-<name>` 功能。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:7
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.discord]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"bot_token = \"...\"                  # create at https://discord.com/"
"developers/applications\n"
"allowed_guilds = [\"123...\"]\n"
"allowed_users = []\n"
"reply_to_mentions_only = true\n"
"draft_update_interval_ms = 750     # bump if hitting Discord rate limits\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.discord]\nenabled = true\nbot_token = \"...\"                  # 在 https://discord.com/developers/applications 创建\nallowed_guilds = [\"123...\"]\nallowed_users = []\nreply_to_mentions_only = true\ndraft_update_interval_ms = 750     # 如果遇到 Discord 速率限制，请增加此值\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:17
msgid ""
"**Bot intents needed:** Message Content Intent, Server Members Intent. Set "
"in the Developer Portal."
msgstr "**所需的机器人意图：** 消息内容意图、服务器成员意图。在开发者门户中设置。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:18
msgid ""
"**[Streaming](../providers/streaming.md):** full — edits messages in place "
"and splits long replies into multiple messages."
msgstr "**[流式传输](../providers/streaming.md)：** 完整模式 — 就地编辑消息，并将长回复拆分为多条消息。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:19
msgid ""
"**Tool-call indicator:** typing indicator while tools run; visible code-"
"block preview for shell and browser calls."
msgstr "**工具调用指示器：** 工具运行时的输入指示器；针对 shell 和浏览器调用的可见代码块预览。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:23
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.slack]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"bot_token = \"xoxb-...\"            # classic bot token\n"
"app_token = \"xapp-...\"            # for Socket Mode\n"
"signing_secret = \"...\"\n"
"allowed_channels = [\"C01...\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.slack]\nenabled = true\nbot_token = \"xoxb-...\"            # 经典机器人令牌\napp_token = \"xapp-...\"            # 用于 Socket 模式\nsigning_secret = \"...\"\nallowed_channels = [\"C01...\"]\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:32
msgid "**Socket Mode** is the default (no public webhook URL needed)."
msgstr "**Socket 模式**是默认模式（无需公共 webhook URL）。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:33
msgid ""
"For HTTP Events API instead, drop `app_token` and point Slack's event "
"subscription URL at `/slack/events` on the gateway."
msgstr "对于 HTTP Events API，请移除 `app_token`，并将 Slack 的事件订阅 URL 指向网关上的 `/slack/events`。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:34
msgid ""
"Supports multi-message streaming, threaded replies, and slash-command "
"ingress."
msgstr "支持多消息流式传输、线程回复和斜杠命令入口。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:38
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.telegram]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"bot_token = \"...\"                  # from @BotFather\n"
"allowed_users = [123456789]\n"
"allowed_chats = [-100987...]       # group / channel IDs\n"
"use_long_polling = true            # default — no webhook needed\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.telegram]\nenabled = true\nbot_token = \"...\"                  # 来自 @BotFather\nallowed_users = [123456789]\nallowed_chats = [-100987...]       # 群组/频道 ID\nuse_long_polling = true            # 默认值 — 无需配置 webhook\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:47
msgid ""
"Long polling is the default; no public URL required. Switch to webhook mode "
"by setting `webhook_url` (then expose the gateway)."
msgstr "长轮询是默认模式，无需公开 URL。通过设置 `webhook_url` 切换到 Webhook 模式（然后暴露网关）。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:48
msgid ""
"Streaming draft edits are supported but capped by Telegram's rate limit. "
"Tune `draft_update_interval_ms` if you see \"Too Many Requests\"."
msgstr "支持流式草稿编辑，但受 Telegram 速率限制的限制。如果看到“Too Many Requests”错误，请调整 `draft_update_interval_ms`。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:52
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.signal]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"phone_number = \"+14155550123\"\n"
"signal_cli_rest_url = \"http://localhost:8080\"   # signal-cli-rest-api "
"service\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.signal]\nenabled = true\nphone_number = \"+14155550123\"\nsignal_cli_rest_url = \"http://localhost:8080\"   # signal-cli-rest-api 服务\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:59
msgid ""
"Signal integration requires running the [signal-cli-rest-api](https://github."
"com/bbernhard/signal-cli-rest-api) container locally — Signal has no "
"official bot API, so we tunnel through `signal-cli`."
msgstr "信号集成需要在本地运行 [signal-cli-rest-api](https://github.com/bbernhard/signal-cli-rest-api) 容器——Signal 没有官方的机器人 API，因此我们通过 `signal-cli` 进行隧道传输。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:61
msgid "iMessage (macOS only)"
msgstr "iMessage（仅限 macOS）"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:63
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.imessage]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"provider = \"linq\"                  # Linq Partner API for iMessage/RCS/"
"SMS\n"
"api_key = \"...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.imessage]\nenabled = true\nprovider = \"linq\"                  # 用于 iMessage/RCS/SMS 的 Linq 合作伙伴 API\napi_key = \"...\"\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:70
msgid ""
"**macOS-only** and requires either Linq as a third-party relay, or direct "
"AppleScript automation (experimental, requires Full Disk Access and "
"Accessibility grants)."
msgstr "**仅限 macOS**，需要 Linq 作为第三方中继，或直接使用 AppleScript 自动化（实验性功能，需要完全磁盘访问权限和辅助功能权限）。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:72
msgid "WeCom (企业微信)"
msgstr "企业微信"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:74
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.wecom]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"corp_id = \"...\"\n"
"corp_secret = \"...\"\n"
"agent_id = 1000001\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.wecom]\nenabled = true\ncorp_id = \"...\"\ncorp_secret = \"...\"\nagent_id = 1000001\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:82
msgid "Chinese enterprise WeChat. Custom app required in the corp admin panel."
msgstr "企业微信。需要在企业后台中创建自定义应用。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:84
msgid "DingTalk"
msgstr "钉钉"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:86
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.dingtalk]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"app_key = \"...\"\n"
"app_secret = \"...\"\n"
"robot_code = \"...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.dingtalk]\nenabled = true\napp_key = \"...\"\napp_secret = \"...\"\nrobot_code = \"...\"\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:94
msgid "Alibaba's enterprise messenger. Same bot shape as WeCom."
msgstr "阿里巴巴的企业通讯工具。与企业微信具有相同的机器人界面。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:96
msgid "Lark / Feishu"
msgstr "飞书"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:98
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.lark]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"app_id = \"...\"\n"
"app_secret = \"...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.lark]\nenabled = true\napp_id = \"...\"\napp_secret = \"...\"\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:105
msgid "QQ"
msgstr "QQ"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:107
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.qq]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"bot_id = \"...\"\n"
"bot_token = \"...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.qq]\nenabled = true\nbot_id = \"...\"\nbot_token = \"...\"\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:114
msgid ""
"Tencent's consumer messenger. Bot API access requires developer registration."
msgstr "腾讯的消费级即时通讯工具。机器人 API 访问需要开发者注册。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:116
msgid "IRC"
msgstr "IRC"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:118
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.irc]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"server = \"irc.libera.chat\"\n"
"port = 6697\n"
"tls = true\n"
"nickname = \"zeroclaw\"\n"
"channels = [\"#mychannel\"]\n"
"nickserv_password = \"...\"          # optional\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.irc]\nenabled = true\nserver = \"irc.libera.chat\"\nport = 6697\ntls = true\nnickname = \"zeroclaw\"\nchannels = [\"#mychannel\"]\nnickserv_password = \"...\"          # 可选\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:129
msgid "Classic IRC. Supports SASL, NickServ auth, and multiple channels."
msgstr "经典 IRC。支持 SASL、NickServ 认证以及多频道。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:131
msgid "Mochat"
msgstr "Mochat"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:133
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.mochat]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"api_key = \"...\"\n"
"# additional provider-specific fields\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.mochat]\nenabled = true\napi_key = \"...\"\n# 其他特定于提供者的字段\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:140
msgid "Notion"
msgstr "Notion"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:142
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.notion]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"integration_token = \"...\"\n"
"databases = [\"...\"]                # DB IDs the agent can write to\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.notion]\nenabled = true\nintegration_token = \"...\"\ndatabases = [\"...\"]                # 智能体可写入的数据库 ID\n```"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:149
msgid ""
"Treats a Notion database as a message surface. Useful for asynchronous "
"workflows where the \"channel\" is a task inbox."
msgstr "将 Notion 数据库视为消息表面。适用于“通道”为任务收件箱的异步工作流。"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:153
msgid "When to prefer a dedicated guide"
msgstr "何时选择专用指南"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:155
msgid ""
"Channels with more intricate setup (OAuth flows, end-to-end encryption, "
"multi-device considerations) live in their own pages:"
msgstr "具有更复杂设置（OAuth 流程、端到端加密、多设备考虑）的频道位于其各自的页面中："

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:157
msgid ""
"[Matrix](./matrix.md) — E2EE, device verification, Synapse/Dendrite specifics"
msgstr "[Matrix](./matrix.md) — E2EE、设备验证、Synapse/Dendrite 特定内容"

#: src/channels/chat-others.md:162
msgid ""
"If you run into configuration friction on any channel above, file an issue "
"with the repro and we'll consider promoting it to a dedicated guide."
msgstr "如果您在上述任何渠道中遇到配置问题，请提交包含复现步骤的 Issue，我们将考虑将其提升为专门的指南。"

#: src/channels/social.md:1
msgid "Social Channels"
msgstr "社交渠道"

#: src/channels/social.md:3
msgid ""
"Broadcast / social-feed integrations. These differ from chat channels in two "
"ways: messages are typically public, and the agent often acts as a poster "
"rather than a bidirectional responder."
msgstr "广播/社交动态集成。与聊天频道不同，这类集成有两个特点：消息通常是公开的，且代理通常充当发布者，而非双向响应者。"

#: src/channels/social.md:5
msgid "Bluesky (AT Protocol)"
msgstr "Bluesky（AT 协议）"

#: src/channels/social.md:7
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.bluesky]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"handle = \"you.bsky.social\"\n"
"app_password = \"xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx\"      # create at bsky.app/settings/"
"app-passwords\n"
"allowed_mentions = [\"@trustedfriend.bsky.social\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.bluesky]\nenabled = true\nhandle = \"you.bsky.social\"\napp_password = \"xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx\"      # 在 bsky.app/settings/app-passwords 创建\nallowed_mentions = [\"@trustedfriend.bsky.social\"]\n```"

#: src/channels/social.md:15
msgid ""
"**Auth:** Bluesky app-password (not your real password). Create one in "
"settings."
msgstr "**认证：** Bluesky 应用密码（不是你的真实密码）。在设置中创建一个。"

#: src/channels/social.md:16
msgid ""
"**Inbound:** mentions and direct messages trigger the agent. Scope with "
"`allowed_mentions`."
msgstr "**入站：** @提及和私信会触发代理。通过 `allowed_mentions` 进行范围限定。"

#: src/channels/social.md:17
msgid "**Outbound:** 300-character posts; longer responses auto-thread."
msgstr "**出站：** 300 字符的帖子；更长的回复会自动分段。"

#: src/channels/social.md:18
msgid "**Protocol:** AT Protocol via `atrium-api` crate."
msgstr "**协议：** 通过 `atrium-api` 库实现的 AT 协议。"

#: src/channels/social.md:22
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.nostr]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"private_key_hex = \"...\"                   # nsec in hex\n"
"relays = [\n"
"    \"wss://relay.damus.io\",\n"
"    \"wss://nos.lol\",\n"
"    \"wss://relay.primal.net\",\n"
"]\n"
"allowed_pubkeys = [\"npub1...\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.nostr]\nenabled = true\nprivate_key_hex = \"...\"                   # nsec in hex\nrelays = [\n    \"wss://relay.damus.io\",\n    \"wss://nos.lol\",\n    \"wss://relay.primal.net\",\n]\nallowed_pubkeys = [\"npub1...\"]\n```"

#: src/channels/social.md:34
msgid ""
"**Auth:** raw private key. Store in the encrypted secrets backend — never in "
"a checked-in config."
msgstr "**Auth：** 原始私钥。请将其存储在加密的密钥后端中，切勿提交到已纳入版本控制的配置文件中。"

#: src/channels/social.md:35
msgid ""
"**Inbound:** kind-1 (text), kind-4 (DM, NIP-04), and kind-1059 (gift-wrap, "
"NIP-17)."
msgstr "**入站消息：** kind-1（文本）、kind-4（DM，NIP-04）和 kind-1059（礼品包装，NIP-17）。"

#: src/channels/social.md:36
msgid "**Outbound:** same kinds. Zap handling is experimental."
msgstr "**出站：** 相同类型。Zap 处理功能处于实验阶段。"

#: src/channels/social.md:37
msgid ""
"**Relays:** the agent connects to all listed relays; use 3–5 for reliability."
msgstr "**中继：** 代理会连接到所有列出的中继；建议使用 3–5 个以确保可靠性。"

#: src/channels/social.md:41
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.twitter]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"api_key = \"...\"\n"
"api_secret = \"...\"\n"
"access_token = \"...\"\n"
"access_secret = \"...\"\n"
"bearer_token = \"...\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.twitter]\nenabled = true\napi_key = \"...\"\napi_secret = \"...\"\naccess_token = \"...\"\naccess_secret = \"...\"\nbearer_token = \"...\"\n```"

#: src/channels/social.md:51
msgid ""
"**Auth:** OAuth 1.0a app credentials. Requires Twitter Developer Portal "
"access — paid tier for full API v2 access."
msgstr "**认证：** OAuth 1.0a 应用凭证。需要 Twitter Developer Portal 访问权限——完整 API v2 访问权限需付费层级。"

#: src/channels/social.md:52
msgid "**Inbound:** mentions via the Filtered Stream endpoint."
msgstr "**入站：** 通过 Filtered Stream 端点提及。"

#: src/channels/social.md:53
msgid "**Outbound:** posts, replies, threads."
msgstr "**出站：**帖子、回复、主题。"

#: src/channels/social.md:54
msgid ""
"**Caveat:** the free tier is rate-limited to the point of near-uselessness. "
"Budget accordingly."
msgstr "**注意：** 免费层的速率限制非常严格，几乎无法正常使用。请据此规划预算。"

#: src/channels/social.md:58
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.reddit]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"client_id = \"...\"\n"
"client_secret = \"...\"\n"
"username = \"...\"\n"
"password = \"...\"                          # or use refresh_token\n"
"user_agent = \"zeroclaw-agent/0.1 by your-username\"\n"
"subreddits = [\"rust\", \"commandline\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.reddit]\nenabled = true\nclient_id = \"...\"\nclient_secret = \"...\"\nusername = \"...\"\npassword = \"...\"                          # 或使用 refresh_token\nuser_agent = \"zeroclaw-agent/0.1 by your-username\"\nsubreddits = [\"rust\", \"commandline\"]\n```"

#: src/channels/social.md:69
msgid ""
"**Auth:** OAuth 2.0 password flow or refresh token. Password flow requires a "
"script-type app."
msgstr "**认证：** OAuth 2.0 密码流或刷新令牌。密码流需要脚本类型的应用。"

#: src/channels/social.md:70
msgid ""
"**Inbound:** new posts and comments in the configured subreddits, plus "
"replies to the agent's own posts."
msgstr "**入站：** 配置子版块中的新帖子和评论，以及对代理自身帖子的回复。"

#: src/channels/social.md:71
msgid "**Outbound:** posts, comments, private messages."
msgstr "**出站：**帖子、评论、私信。"

#: src/channels/social.md:72
msgid ""
"**User-agent convention:** Reddit's API requires a descriptive user-agent "
"string. Non-compliance → rate limits."
msgstr "**用户代理约定：** Reddit 的 API 要求提供描述性的用户代理字符串。不遵守此规定会导致速率限制。"

#: src/channels/social.md:76
msgid "Operating social channels safely"
msgstr "安全地运营社交媒体渠道"

#: src/channels/social.md:78
msgid ""
"Bots on public social networks attract adversarial input. Two precautions:"
msgstr "公共社交网络上的机器人会吸引对抗性输入。两个预防措施："

#: src/channels/social.md:80
msgid ""
"**Restrict who the agent will respond to.** Use `allowed_mentions` / "
"`allowed_pubkeys` / `allowed_users` to whitelist. The default empty-list "
"behaviour varies per channel — check each."
msgstr "**限制代理将响应的对象。** 使用 `allowed_mentions` / `allowed_pubkeys` / `allowed_users` 进行白名单设置。默认的空白列表行为因频道而异——请逐一检查。"

#: src/channels/social.md:81
msgid ""
"**Keep autonomy level at `Supervised` or lower.** A public-facing agent in "
"`Full` autonomy is effectively a public shell. If you want to run public-"
"facing, disable shell tools for that channel:"
msgstr "**将自主级别保持在 `Supervised` 或更低。** 在 `Full` 自主级别下，面向公众的代理实际上等同于一个公共 shell。如果您希望运行面向公众的代理，请为该通道禁用 shell 工具："

#: src/channels/social.md:83
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.bluesky]\n"
"tools_allow = [\"http\", \"web_search\"]      # whitelist — no shell, no "
"file_write\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.bluesky]\ntools_allow = [\"http\", \"web_search\"]      # 白名单 — 不允许 shell 和 file_write\n```"

#: src/channels/social.md:88
msgid "Rate limits and backoff"
msgstr "速率限制与退避"

#: src/channels/social.md:90
msgid ""
"All social channels are subject to aggressive rate limits. ZeroClaw's "
"outbound queue uses exponential backoff on 429 responses. If you hit "
"persistent rate-limiting, lower `draft_update_interval_ms` and check whether "
"you're accidentally editing messages (Bluesky does not support edits; others "
"have per-operation limits)."
msgstr "所有社交频道都受到严格的速率限制。ZeroClaw 的出站队列在收到 429 响应时会使用指数退避策略。如果遇到持续的速率限制，请降低 `draft_update_interval_ms` 的值，并检查是否意外编辑了消息（Bluesky 不支持编辑；其他平台对每次操作有限制）。"

#: src/channels/email.md:3
msgid ""
"Two email channels depending on how you want inbound messages delivered."
msgstr "两个电子邮件通道，具体取决于您希望如何接收传入消息。"

#: src/channels/email.md:5
msgid "IMAP + SMTP (`email_channel`)"
msgstr "IMAP + SMTP（`email_channel`）"

#: src/channels/email.md:7
msgid ""
"The general-purpose email channel. Polls IMAP for new messages, sends via "
"SMTP. Works with Gmail, Outlook, Fastmail, self-hosted Postfix, and anything "
"else that speaks IMAP/SMTP."
msgstr "通用电子邮件通道。轮询 IMAP 以获取新邮件，通过 SMTP 发送。支持 Gmail、Outlook、Fastmail、自托管的 Postfix 以及其他任何支持 IMAP/SMTP 的服务。"

#: src/channels/email.md:9
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.email]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"\n"
"[channels.email.imap]\n"
"host = \"imap.example.com\"\n"
"port = 993\n"
"username = \"you@example.com\"\n"
"password = \"...\"                 # or app-password for Gmail/iCloud\n"
"mailbox = \"INBOX\"\n"
"poll_interval_secs = 60\n"
"\n"
"[channels.email.smtp]\n"
"host = \"smtp.example.com\"\n"
"port = 587\n"
"username = \"you@example.com\"\n"
"password = \"...\"\n"
"\n"
"[channels.email.filter]\n"
"allowed_senders = [\"boss@example.com\", \"alerts@example.com\"]\n"
"subject_prefix = \"[agent]\"       # only respond to subjects starting with "
"this\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.email]\nenabled = true\n\n[channels.email.imap]\nhost = \"imap.example.com\"\nport = 993\nusername = \"you@example.com\"\npassword = \"...\"                 # 或 Gmail/iCloud 的应用专用密码\nmailbox = \"INBOX\"\npoll_interval_secs = 60\n\n[channels.email.smtp]\nhost = \"smtp.example.com\"\nport = 587\nusername = \"you@example.com\"\npassword = \"...\"\n\n[channels.email.filter]\nallowed_senders = [\"boss@example.com\", \"alerts@example.com\"]\nsubject_prefix = \"[agent]\"       # 仅响应以此开头的主旨\n```"

#: src/channels/email.md:32
msgid "Gmail gotchas"
msgstr "Gmail 注意事项"

#: src/channels/email.md:34
msgid ""
"**App passwords required** if 2FA is on. Regular account password is "
"rejected."
msgstr "如果启用了双因素身份验证（2FA），则必须使用应用专用密码。常规账户密码将被拒绝。"

#: src/channels/email.md:35
msgid "**\"Less secure app access\" is gone** — app password is the only path."
msgstr "**“安全性较低的应用程序访问权限”已移除** — 应用专用密码是唯一途径。"

#: src/channels/email.md:36
msgid ""
"Consider the Gmail Push channel below for real-time delivery instead of "
"polling."
msgstr "考虑使用 Gmail 推送通道进行实时投递，而不是轮询。"

#: src/channels/email.md:38
msgid "Outlook / Office 365"
msgstr "Outlook / Office 365"

#: src/channels/email.md:40
msgid "OAuth 2.0 is recommended over password auth:"
msgstr "推荐使用 OAuth 2.0 而非密码认证："

#: src/channels/email.md:42
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.email.imap]\n"
"host = \"outlook.office365.com\"\n"
"port = 993\n"
"username = \"you@example.com\"\n"
"oauth_token = \"...\"              # managed via `zeroclaw channel auth "
"email`\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.email.imap]\nhost = \"outlook.office365.com\"\nport = 993\nusername = \"you@example.com\"\noauth_token = \"...\"              # 通过 `zeroclaw channel auth email` 管理\n```"

#: src/channels/email.md:50
msgid "Gmail Push (`gmail_push`)"
msgstr "Gmail 推送 (`gmail_push`)"

#: src/channels/email.md:52
msgid "Real-time delivery via Google Cloud Pub/Sub — no polling."
msgstr "通过 Google Cloud Pub/Sub 实现实时交付——无需轮询。"

#: src/channels/email.md:54
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.gmail_push]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"account = \"you@gmail.com\"\n"
"client_secret_json = \"~/.zeroclaw/gmail-client-secret.json\"\n"
"pubsub_topic = \"projects/my-project/topics/gmail-inbox\"\n"
"pubsub_subscription = \"projects/my-project/subscriptions/zeroclaw-sub\"\n"
"allowed_senders = [\"boss@example.com\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.gmail_push]\nenabled = true\naccount = \"you@gmail.com\"\nclient_secret_json = \"~/.zeroclaw/gmail-client-secret.json\"\npubsub_topic = \"projects/my-project/topics/gmail-inbox\"\npubsub_subscription = \"projects/my-project/subscriptions/zeroclaw-sub\"\nallowed_senders = [\"boss@example.com\"]\n```"

#: src/channels/email.md:66
msgid "Create a Google Cloud project, enable Gmail API and Pub/Sub API"
msgstr "创建 Google Cloud 项目，启用 Gmail API 和 Pub/Sub API"

#: src/channels/email.md:67
msgid "Create a Pub/Sub topic the Gmail service can publish to"
msgstr "创建一个 Gmail 服务可以发布消息的 Pub/Sub 主题"

#: src/channels/email.md:68
msgid "Create a pull subscription on that topic for ZeroClaw"
msgstr "为 ZeroClaw 在该主题上创建拉取订阅"

#: src/channels/email.md:69
msgid "Create OAuth client credentials (desktop app type), download JSON"
msgstr "创建 OAuth 客户端凭据（桌面应用类型），下载 JSON"

#: src/channels/email.md:70
msgid ""
"On first run, `zeroclaw channel auth gmail-push` opens a browser for the "
"OAuth consent"
msgstr "首次运行时，`zeroclaw channel auth gmail-push` 会打开浏览器以进行 OAuth 同意"

#: src/channels/email.md:71
msgid "The agent watches the subscription for new-mail notifications"
msgstr "代理会监视订阅以获取新邮件通知"

#: src/channels/email.md:73
msgid ""
"Outbound sends still go via SMTP — configure an `smtp` block in this channel "
"the same way as the IMAP+SMTP channel."
msgstr "出站发送仍然通过 SMTP 进行——在此通道中配置 `smtp` 块的方式与 IMAP+SMTP 通道相同。"

#: src/channels/email.md:77
msgid "Reply threading"
msgstr "回复线程"

#: src/channels/email.md:79
msgid ""
"Both email channels thread replies using `In-Reply-To` and `References` "
"headers so conversations stay grouped in whatever client the sender uses."
msgstr "两个电子邮件通道均使用 `In-Reply-To` 和 `References` 标头来线程化回复，以便在发件人使用的任何客户端中保持对话分组。"

#: src/channels/email.md:81
msgid "Attachment handling"
msgstr "附件处理"

#: src/channels/email.md:83
msgid ""
"Inbound attachments are stored under `<workspace>/attachments/<conversation>/"
"`. The agent gets file paths in its context and can read them via the "
"`file_read` tool."
msgstr "传入的附件存储在 `<workspace>/attachments/<conversation>/` 下。代理会在其上下文中获取文件路径，并可以通过 `file_read` 工具读取这些文件。"

#: src/channels/email.md:85
msgid ""
"Outbound attachments are not supported yet — the agent replies with links to "
"files in the workspace, and the user downloads via whatever tunnel the "
"workspace is exposed through."
msgstr "暂不支持出站附件——代理会回复工作区中的文件链接，用户通过工作区暴露的任意隧道进行下载。"

#: src/channels/email.md:87
msgid "Rate and volume limits"
msgstr "速率和体积限制"

#: src/channels/email.md:89
msgid "Email isn't optimised for conversational latency. Expect:"
msgstr "电子邮件并不适合对话式延迟。预期："

#: src/channels/email.md:91
msgid ""
"IMAP poll latency: `poll_interval_secs` (default 60 s). Lower at the cost of "
"server load; some providers rate-limit aggressive polling."
msgstr "IMAP 轮询延迟：`poll_interval_secs`（默认 60 秒）。降低该值会增加服务器负载；部分提供商会对过于频繁的轮询进行速率限制。"

#: src/channels/email.md:92
msgid ""
"SMTP send: subject to your provider's daily-send quota (Gmail: 500/day for "
"free accounts, 2000/day for Workspace)."
msgstr "SMTP 发送：受限于您的提供商的每日发送配额（Gmail：免费账户每天 500 封，Workspace 账户每天 2000 封）。"

#: src/channels/email.md:94 src/hardware/index.md:67
msgid "Safety"
msgstr "安全"

#: src/channels/email.md:96
msgid ""
"Email has no auth at the protocol level beyond SMTP's envelope — anyone can "
"claim to be anyone. Always configure `allowed_senders` (strict list of "
"addresses) or `subject_prefix` (shared secret in the subject line) before "
"exposing the agent to an inbox that receives public mail."
msgstr "电子邮件在协议层面除了 SMTP 信封之外没有身份验证机制——任何人都可以冒充任何人。在向接收公共邮件的邮箱暴露代理之前，请务必配置 `allowed_senders`（严格的地址列表）或 `subject_prefix`（主题行中的共享密钥）。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:1
msgid "Voice & Telephony"
msgstr "语音与电话"

#: src/channels/voice.md:3
msgid ""
"Real-time voice input and output. Four channels cover the matrix: inbound "
"calls, outbound speech synthesis, local microphone wake, and SIP-grade real-"
"time conversation."
msgstr "实时语音输入和输出。四个通道覆盖矩阵：入站呼叫、出站语音合成、本地麦克风唤醒以及 SIP 级实时对话。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:5
msgid "ClawdTalk (real-time SIP)"
msgstr "ClawdTalk（实时 SIP）"

#: src/channels/voice.md:7
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.clawdtalk]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"telnyx_api_key = \"...\"\n"
"connection_id = \"...\"              # Telnyx SIP connection\n"
"model_provider = \"voice-brain\"     # references [providers.models.voice-"
"brain]\n"
"voice = \"Polly.Joanna-Neural\"      # Telnyx voice ID\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.clawdtalk]\nenabled = true\ntelnyx_api_key = \"...\"\nconnection_id = \"...\"              # Telnyx SIP 连接\nmodel_provider = \"voice-brain\"     # 引用 [providers.models.voice-brain]\nvoice = \"Polly.Joanna-Neural\"      # Telnyx 语音 ID\n```"

#: src/channels/voice.md:16
msgid ""
"Full-duplex SIP voice powered by Telnyx. The agent talks over a real phone "
"call — inbound or outbound. Supports barge-in, mid-turn tool use, and "
"regional number provisioning."
msgstr "由 Telnyx 提供支持的全双工 SIP 语音。代理通过真实电话通话（入站或出站）进行交流。支持打断、中途工具调用和区域号码配置。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:18
msgid ""
"**Pair with:** a `telnyx` provider for the brain (`crates/zeroclaw-providers/"
"src/telnyx.rs`) and ensure your Telnyx account has a SIP connection with the "
"correct webhook URL pointed at the ZeroClaw gateway."
msgstr "**配对：** 为大脑（`crates/zeroclaw-providers/src/telnyx.rs`）使用 `telnyx` 提供程序，并确保你的 Telnyx 账户中有一个 SIP 连接，其 webhook URL 指向 ZeroClaw 网关。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:20
msgid "Voice Call (Twilio / Telnyx / Plivo)"
msgstr "语音通话（Twilio / Telnyx / Plivo）"

#: src/channels/voice.md:22
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.voice_call]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"carrier = \"twilio\"                 # or \"telnyx\", \"plivo\"\n"
"account_sid = \"...\"\n"
"auth_token = \"...\"\n"
"from_number = \"+14155550123\"\n"
"stt_provider = \"whisper\"\n"
"tts_provider = \"elevenlabs\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.voice_call]\nenabled = true\ncarrier = \"twilio\"                 # 或 \"telnyx\", \"plivo\"\naccount_sid = \"...\"\nauth_token = \"...\"\nfrom_number = \"+14155550123\"\nstt_provider = \"whisper\"\ntts_provider = \"elevenlabs\"\n```"

#: src/channels/voice.md:33
msgid ""
"Traditional carrier voice — the agent picks up, transcribes with STT, "
"replies with TTS. Higher latency than ClawdTalk but works with any regular "
"phone number and doesn't require SIP trunk provisioning."
msgstr "传统运营商语音——代理接听，通过 STT 进行转录，再通过 TTS 回复。延迟高于 ClawdTalk，但适用于任何普通电话号码，且无需 SIP 中继配置。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:35
msgid "Voice Wake (local wake-word)"
msgstr "语音唤醒（本地唤醒词）"

#: src/channels/voice.md:37
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.voice_wake]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"wake_phrase = \"hey claw\"\n"
"engine = \"porcupine\"               # or \"openwakeword\"\n"
"model_path = \"~/.zeroclaw/wake/hey-claw.ppn\"\n"
"audio_device = \"default\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.voice_wake]\nenabled = true\nwake_phrase = \"hey claw\"\nengine = \"porcupine\"               # 或 \"openwakeword\"\nmodel_path = \"~/.zeroclaw/wake/hey-claw.ppn\"\naudio_device = \"default\"\n```"

#: src/channels/voice.md:46
msgid ""
"Runs locally, listens on the mic, triggers agent interaction when it hears "
"the wake phrase. Useful for:"
msgstr "在本地运行，监听麦克风，在听到唤醒词时触发代理交互。适用于："

#: src/channels/voice.md:48
msgid "Physical voice assistants on SBCs"
msgstr "SBC 上的物理语音助手"

#: src/channels/voice.md:49
msgid "Desktop \"hotword → ask\" workflows"
msgstr "桌面端“热词 → 提问”工作流"

#: src/channels/voice.md:50
msgid "Always-listening home-automation agents"
msgstr "始终在线的家庭自动化代理"

#: src/channels/voice.md:52
msgid ""
"The agent doesn't send audio anywhere — wake detection is local. Only post-"
"wake speech goes through STT and reaches the LLM."
msgstr "代理不会将音频发送到任何地方——唤醒检测是本地进行的。只有唤醒后的语音会通过 STT 并到达 LLM。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:54
msgid "TTS (outbound speech synthesis)"
msgstr "TTS（出站语音合成）"

#: src/channels/voice.md:56
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.tts]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"engine = \"piper\"                   # local, free\n"
"voice = \"en_US-lessac-medium\"\n"
"output_device = \"default\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.tts]\nenabled = true\nengine = \"piper\"                   # 本地，免费\nvoice = \"en_US-lessac-medium\"\noutput_device = \"default\"\n```"

#: src/channels/voice.md:64
msgid "Other engines:"
msgstr "其他引擎："

#: src/channels/voice.md:66
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.tts]\n"
"engine = \"openai\"                  # TTS-1 or TTS-1-HD\n"
"voice = \"alloy\"\n"
"api_key = \"...\"\n"
"\n"
"[channels.tts]\n"
"engine = \"elevenlabs\"\n"
"voice_id = \"21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM\"\n"
"api_key = \"...\"\n"
"\n"
"[channels.tts]\n"
"engine = \"google-cloud\"\n"
"voice = \"en-US-Neural2-J\"\n"
"credentials_json = \"~/.zeroclaw/gcp.json\"\n"
"\n"
"[channels.tts]\n"
"engine = \"edge\"                    # Microsoft Edge TTS — free, online\n"
"voice = \"en-US-AndrewNeural\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.tts]\nengine = \"openai\"                  # TTS-1 或 TTS-1-HD\nvoice = \"alloy\"\napi_key = \"...\"\n\n[channels.tts]\nengine = \"elevenlabs\"\nvoice_id = \"21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM\"\napi_key = \"...\"\n\n[channels.tts]\nengine = \"google-cloud\"\nvoice = \"en-US-Neural2-J\"\ncredentials_json = \"~/.zeroclaw/gcp.json\"\n\n[channels.tts]\nengine = \"edge\"                    # Microsoft Edge TTS — 免费，在线\nvoice = \"en-US-AndrewNeural\"\n```"

#: src/channels/voice.md:87
msgid ""
"TTS is output-only — it's not a conversation channel; it's a speaker for "
"other channels' replies. Pair with `voice_wake` for a complete local voice "
"assistant."
msgstr "TTS 仅用于输出——它不是对话通道，而是其他通道回复的扬声器。与 `voice_wake` 配合使用，即可构建完整的本地语音助手。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:91
msgid "Latency budget"
msgstr "延迟预算"

#: src/channels/voice.md:93
msgid "Speech feels real-time below ~500 ms end-to-end. Practical budgets:"
msgstr "端到端延迟低于约 500 毫秒时，语音听起来是实时的。实际预算："

