msgstr "`deepgram` — 实时流式语音转文本（最快）"

#: src/channels/voice.md:112
msgid "`google-cloud-stt`"
msgstr "`google-cloud-stt`"

#: src/channels/voice.md:113
msgid "`azure-stt`"
msgstr "`azure-stt`"

#: src/channels/voice.md:115
msgid "Set in the voice channel's config (`stt_provider = \"deepgram\"`)."
msgstr "设置在语音频道的配置中（`stt_provider = \"deepgram\"`）。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:117
msgid "Hardware notes"
msgstr "硬件说明"

#: src/channels/voice.md:119
msgid "For always-on voice on an SBC:"
msgstr "对于始终开启的语音功能，在 SBC 上："

#: src/channels/voice.md:121
msgid ""
"USB mic: any UAC-compliant mic works. `arecord -l` to verify the OS sees it"
msgstr "USB 麦克风：任何符合 UAC 标准的麦克风均可使用。运行 `arecord -l` 以验证操作系统是否已识别该设备。"

#: src/channels/voice.md:122
msgid ""
"Speaker: either USB audio out or the SBC's onboard jack; set `output_device` "
"to the ALSA name"
msgstr "扬声器：可以是 USB 音频输出或 SBC 板载插孔；将 `output_device` 设置为 ALSA 名称"

#: src/channels/voice.md:123
msgid ""
"Microphones with built-in AEC (acoustic echo cancellation) dramatically "
"improve wake reliability when the speaker is nearby"
msgstr "内置 AEC（声学回声消除）功能的麦克风在扬声器靠近时能显著提高唤醒可靠性"

#: src/channels/voice.md:125
msgid ""
"See [Hardware → Android](../hardware/android-setup.md) for Android-specific "
"audio setup."
msgstr "有关 Android 特定的音频设置，请参阅 [硬件 → Android](../hardware/android-setup.md)。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:3
msgid ""
"A generic inbound HTTP channel. Any service that can POST a JSON payload "
"(GitHub, Linear, Sentry, Zapier, cron-job.org, your own scripts) can hand "
"work to the agent via a webhook URL."
msgstr "一个通用的入站 HTTP 通道。任何能够 POST JSON 负载的服务（如 GitHub、Linear、Sentry、Zapier、cron-job.org 或你自己的脚本）都可以通过 webhook URL 将工作交给代理。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:5
msgid ""
"Webhooks live inside the gateway — if the gateway is running, webhooks are "
"reachable at `/webhook/<name>`."
msgstr "Webhooks 位于网关内部——如果网关正在运行，Webhooks 可通过 `/webhook/<name>` 访问。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:9
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.webhooks.github-issues]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"secret = \"...\"                    # HMAC secret for signature "
"verification\n"
"dispatch_to = \"sop:triage-issue\"  # or a conversation ID, or a system "
"prompt\n"
"allow_list = [\"github.com\"]       # enforce source IP allowlist\n"
"\n"
"[channels.webhooks.grafana]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"secret = \"...\"\n"
"dispatch_to = \"cron:alert-handler\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.webhooks.github-issues]\nenabled = true\nsecret = \"...\"                    # 用于签名验证的 HMAC 密钥\ndispatch_to = \"sop:triage-issue\"  # 或对话 ID，或系统提示词\nallow_list = [\"github.com\"]       # 强制实施源 IP 白名单\n\n[channels.webhooks.grafana]\nenabled = true\nsecret = \"...\"\ndispatch_to = \"cron:alert-handler\"\n```"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:22
msgid "The `dispatch_to` field points the inbound event at one of:"
msgstr "`dispatch_to` 字段将入站事件指向以下之一："

#: src/channels/webhook.md:24
msgid ""
"`sop:<name>` — runs a Standard Operating Procedure with the payload as input"
msgstr "`sop:<name>` — 以有效载荷作为输入运行标准操作程序"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:25
msgid "`cron:<name>` — triggers a scheduled job off-schedule"
msgstr "`cron:<name>` — 触发计划外执行的定时任务"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:26
msgid ""
"`conversation:<id>` — appends to a named conversation (agent responds "
"normally)"
msgstr "`conversation:<id>` — 追加到指定名称的对话中（代理正常响应）"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:27
msgid ""
"`system:<prompt>` — runs a one-shot agent call with the payload appended to "
"a system prompt"
msgstr "`system:<prompt>` — 使用附加到系统提示的有效载荷执行一次性代理调用"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:31
msgid ""
"GitHub, Stripe, Slack, and most major sources sign webhooks with HMAC. Set "
"`secret` to the shared secret; the channel verifies `X-Hub-Signature-256` / "
"`X-Signature` / equivalent before dispatching."
msgstr "GitHub、Stripe、Slack 以及大多数主要来源均使用 HMAC 对 Webhook 进行签名。将 `secret` 设置为共享密钥；通道在分发前会验证 `X-Hub-Signature-256` / `X-Signature` / 等效签名头。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:33
msgid ""
"Sources without signing (open webhooks) should at minimum set `allow_list` "
"to restrict by source IP. A webhook URL with no auth and no IP allowlist is "
"an open ingress — don't."
msgstr "未签名的源（开放 Webhook）至少应设置 `allow_list` 以限制来源 IP。没有身份验证且没有 IP 白名单的 Webhook URL 相当于开放入口——请勿这样做。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:35
msgid "Shape of what the agent sees"
msgstr "智能体所见的形状"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:37
msgid ""
"By default the agent receives the raw JSON payload as a user message. For "
"structured sources, use `template`:"
msgstr "默认情况下，代理会将原始 JSON 负载作为用户消息接收。对于结构化源，请使用 `template`："

#: src/channels/webhook.md:39
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.webhooks.sentry]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"secret = \"...\"\n"
"dispatch_to = \"sop:investigate-error\"\n"
"template = \"\"\"\n"
"New Sentry alert:\n"
"Level: {{ payload.level }}\n"
"Title: {{ payload.title }}\n"
"URL: {{ payload.web_url }}\n"
"\n"
"Stack:\n"
"{{ payload.exception.values[0].stacktrace }}\n"
"\"\"\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.webhooks.sentry]\nenabled = true\nsecret = \"...\"\ndispatch_to = \"sop:investigate-error\"\ntemplate = \"\"\"\n新的 Sentry 告警：\n级别：{{ payload.level }}\n标题：{{ payload.title }}\nURL：{{ payload.web_url }}\n\n堆栈：\n{{ payload.exception.values[0].stacktrace }}\n\"\"\"\n```"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:55
msgid ""
"Templates use MiniJinja; `payload` is the full JSON body, plus `headers` and "
"`query` for URL params."
msgstr "模板使用 MiniJinja；`payload` 是完整的 JSON 主体，以及用于 URL 参数的 `headers` 和 `query`。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:57
msgid "Replies"
msgstr "回复"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:59
msgid ""
"Webhook channels default to one-shot: the agent handles the event, writes to "
"the receipts log, and returns 200. For webhook sources that wait for a reply "
"(interactive bots, slash commands), set `reply_mode`:"
msgstr "Webhook 通道默认为一次性模式：代理处理事件，写入收据日志，并返回 200。对于需要等待回复的 Webhook 源（交互式机器人、斜杠命令），请设置 `reply_mode`："

#: src/channels/webhook.md:61
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[channels.webhooks.slack-slash]\n"
"enabled = true\n"
"secret = \"...\"\n"
"reply_mode = \"inline-json\"        # respond to POST with {\"text\": \"..."
"\"}\n"
"template = \"{{ payload.text }}\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[channels.webhooks.slack-slash]\nenabled = true\nsecret = \"...\"\nreply_mode = \"inline-json\"        # 使用 {\"text\": \"...\"} 响应 POST 请求\ntemplate = \"{{ payload.text }}\"\n```"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:69
msgid ""
"Supported reply modes: `status-only` (default, 200 OK), `inline-json`, "
"`inline-text`."
msgstr "支持的回复模式：`status-only`（默认，200 OK）、`inline-json`、`inline-text`。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:71
msgid "Public exposure"
msgstr "公开暴露"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:73
msgid ""
"By default the gateway binds to localhost only. To expose webhooks publicly:"
msgstr "默认情况下，网关仅绑定到 localhost。若要公开暴露 Webhook："

#: src/channels/webhook.md:75
msgid ""
"**Reverse proxy** — run nginx / Caddy / Traefik in front, terminate TLS, "
"proxy to localhost. See [Operations → Network deployment](../ops/network-"
"deployment.md)."
msgstr "**反向代理** — 在前方运行 nginx / Caddy / Traefik，终止 TLS，并代理到 localhost。请参阅 [操作 → 网络部署](../ops/network-deployment.md)。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:76
msgid ""
"**Tunnel** — configure `[tunnel] provider = \"ngrok\" | \"cloudflare\" | "
"\"tailscale\"` and restart the daemon. Tunnels start alongside the gateway."
msgstr "**隧道** — 配置 `[tunnel] provider = \"ngrok\" | \"cloudflare\" | \"tailscale\"` 并重启守护进程。隧道将与网关一同启动。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:77
msgid ""
"**Public bind** — set `ZEROCLAW_ALLOW_PUBLIC_BIND=1` and `[gateway] host = "
"\"0.0.0.0\"`. Not recommended without a firewall in front."
msgstr "**公开绑定** — 设置 `ZEROCLAW_ALLOW_PUBLIC_BIND=1` 和 `[gateway] host = \"0.0.0.0\"`。不建议在没有前置防火墙的情况下使用。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:79
msgid "Rate limiting"
msgstr "速率限制"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:81
msgid ""
"The webhook channel applies a per-webhook-name rate limit (default 10/s). "
"Override:"
msgstr "Webhook 通道会对每个 webhook 名称应用速率限制（默认 10/s）。覆盖："

#: src/channels/webhook.md:88
msgid "Excess requests return 429."
msgstr "超出限制的请求将返回 429。"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:90
msgid "Code"
msgstr "代码"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:92
msgid ""
"Channel: `crates/zeroclaw-channels/src/webhook.rs` (plus gateway ingress in "
"`crates/zeroclaw-gateway/`)"
msgstr "通道：`crates/zeroclaw-channels/src/webhook.rs`（以及 `crates/zeroclaw-gateway/` 中的网关入口）"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:93
msgid "Templates: `crates/zeroclaw-runtime/src/templating.rs`"
msgstr "模板：`crates/zeroclaw-runtime/src/templating.rs`"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:97
msgid "[Operations → Network deployment](../ops/network-deployment.md)"
msgstr "[操作 → 网络部署](../ops/network-deployment.md)"

#: src/channels/webhook.md:98
msgid "[SOP → Connectivity](../sop/connectivity.md) — webhook + SOP patterns"
msgstr "[SOP → 连接性](../sop/connectivity.md) — webhook + SOP 模式"

#: src/channels/acp.md:1
msgid "ACP — Agent Client Protocol"
msgstr "ACP — 代理客户端协议"

#: src/channels/acp.md:3
msgid ""
"**ACP** is a JSON-RPC 2.0 protocol over stdio that lets editors and IDEs "
"talk to a running ZeroClaw agent as a session host. Newline-delimited JSON — "
"lightweight, streamable, easy to wire to a subprocess."
msgstr "**ACP** 是一个基于 stdio 的 JSON-RPC 2.0 协议，允许编辑器和 IDE 与正在运行的 ZeroClaw 代理作为会话主机进行通信。采用换行符分隔的 JSON（newline-delimited JSON）——轻量级、可流式传输、易于与子进程集成。"

#: src/channels/acp.md:5
msgid ""
"Think of it as \"LSP for agents\": the editor launches `zeroclaw acp`, sends "
"prompts over stdin, receives session updates on stdout."
msgstr "将其视为“面向智能体的 LSP”：编辑器启动 `zeroclaw acp`，通过标准输入发送提示，通过标准输出接收会话更新。"

#: src/channels/acp.md:7
msgid "What you'd use it for"
msgstr "你打算用它做什么"

#: src/channels/acp.md:9
msgid ""
"An editor extension that offers an \"ask the agent about this file\" command"
msgstr "一个提供“向代理询问此文件”命令的编辑器扩展"

#: src/channels/acp.md:10
msgid ""
"A terminal multiplexer integration that opens a side pane with an agent "
"session"
msgstr "集成终端复用器，打开带有代理会话的侧边窗格"

#: src/channels/acp.md:11
msgid ""
"A CI runner that drives the agent programmatically without a full gateway "
"setup"
msgstr "一个通过编程方式驱动代理的 CI 运行器，无需完整的网关设置"

#: src/channels/acp.md:12
msgid ""
"Anything that wants agent sessions without HTTP and without binding a port"
msgstr "任何希望在不使用 HTTP 且无需绑定端口的情况下使用代理会话的功能"

