#: src/ops/overview.md:1
msgid "Operations — Overview"
msgstr "操作 — 概述"

#: src/ops/overview.md:3
msgid ""
"How to run ZeroClaw in production. The surface is intentionally small: one "
"binary, one config file, one SQLite workspace. Most \"operations\" is "
"\"systemd and journald\"."
msgstr "如何在生产环境中运行 ZeroClaw。其表面 intentionally small：一个二进制文件，一个配置文件，一个 SQLite 工作区。大多数“操作”是“systemd 和 journald”。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:5
msgid "This section covers:"
msgstr "本节涵盖："

#: src/ops/overview.md:7
msgid "[Service & daemon](./service.md) — keeping the process alive"
msgstr "[服务与守护进程](./service.md) — 保持进程运行"

