#: src/ops/overview.md:100
msgid ""
"Blocks and denials are worth looking at — if the agent is repeatedly hitting "
"the same policy block, either your policy is wrong or your agent is "
"misbehaving."
msgstr "值得查看阻止和拒绝的情况——如果代理反复遇到相同的策略阻止，那么可能是你的策略有误，或者代理行为不当。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:102
msgid "Capacity"
msgstr "容量"

#: src/ops/overview.md:104
msgid "A single ZeroClaw instance can handle:"
msgstr "单个 ZeroClaw 实例可以处理："

#: src/ops/overview.md:106
msgid "Multiple concurrent conversations across all channels"
msgstr "跨所有频道的多个并发对话"

#: src/ops/overview.md:107
msgid "Tool calls at whatever rate the provider and sandbox allow"
msgstr "以提供商和沙箱允许的任意速率进行工具调用"

#: src/ops/overview.md:108
msgid "Long-running agent loops (tool chains of 20+ calls)"
msgstr "长时间运行的智能体循环（包含 20 多次调用的工具链）"

#: src/ops/overview.md:110
msgid ""
"Scale laterally by running one instance per workspace. Don't try to run two "
"daemons on the same workspace — SQLite's single-writer model will produce "
"lock contention and ultimately corruption."
msgstr "通过在每个工作区运行一个实例来实现横向扩展。不要尝试在同一工作区运行两个守护进程——SQLite 的单写者模型会导致锁争用并最终造成数据损坏。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:112
msgid ""
"For multi-tenant hosting, see the proposal in #2765 (closed, historical — "
"the architecture for in-process multi-workspace routing)."
msgstr "有关多租户托管，请参阅 #2765 中的提案（已关闭，历史记录 — 用于进程内多工作区路由的架构）。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:114
msgid "Backups"
msgstr "备份"

#: src/ops/overview.md:116
msgid "What to back up:"
msgstr "需要备份的内容："

#: src/ops/overview.md:118
msgid ""
"`~/.zeroclaw/config.toml` — contains channel credentials (encrypted if using "
"secrets store)"
msgstr "`~/.zeroclaw/config.toml` — 包含频道凭据（如果使用密钥存储，则为加密状态）"

#: src/ops/overview.md:119
msgid "`~/.zeroclaw/workspace/*.db` — SQLite conversation memory"
msgstr "`~/.zeroclaw/workspace/*.db` — SQLite 对话记忆"

#: src/ops/overview.md:120
msgid ""
"`~/.zeroclaw/secrets.key` — master key for the encrypted secrets store (if "
"used). **Without it, the config's secrets are unrecoverable.**"
msgstr "`~/.zeroclaw/secrets.key` — 加密密钥存储的主密钥（如果使用）。**没有它，配置文件中的密钥将无法恢复。**"

#: src/ops/overview.md:121
msgid "`~/.zeroclaw/workspace/receipts/` — tool-receipts log"
msgstr "`~/.zeroclaw/workspace/receipts/` — 工具收据日志"

#: src/ops/overview.md:123
msgid ""
"A plain `tar czf zeroclaw-$(date +%F).tar.gz ~/.zeroclaw` covers everything. "
"Restic, borg, or Duplicacy work fine for incremental backups."
msgstr "一条简单的 `tar czf zeroclaw-$(date +%F).tar.gz ~/.zeroclaw` 命令即可覆盖所有内容。对于增量备份，Restic、borg 或 Duplicacy 都能很好地工作。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:125
msgid ""
"**Do not back up `~/.zeroclaw/workspace/cache/`** — it's regenerable and can "
"be large."
msgstr "**不要备份 `~/.zeroclaw/workspace/cache/`** — 该目录可重新生成，且可能占用大量空间。"

#: src/ops/overview.md:127
msgid "Updates"
msgstr "更新"

#: src/ops/overview.md:129
msgid ""
"The service does not auto-update. Subscribe to the release feed (GitHub "
"releases or the Discord `#releases` channel — see [Contributing → "
"Communication](../contributing/communication.md)). Typical update cadence:"
msgstr "该服务不会自动更新。请订阅发布频道（GitHub Releases 或 Discord 的 `#releases` 频道 — 参见 [贡献指南 → 沟通](../contributing/communication.md)）。典型的更新频率为："

#: src/ops/overview.md:131
msgid "Read the release notes"
msgstr "阅读发布说明"

#: src/ops/overview.md:132
msgid "Back up `~/.zeroclaw/`"
msgstr "备份 `~/.zeroclaw/`"

#: src/ops/overview.md:133
msgid ""
"Update the binary (`brew upgrade`, bootstrap re-run, or `cargo install --"
"force`)"
msgstr "更新二进制文件（`brew upgrade`、重新运行引导程序，或 `cargo install --force`）"

#: src/ops/overview.md:135
msgid "Verify `/health/*` endpoints return green"
msgstr "验证 `/health/*` 端点返回绿色"

#: src/ops/overview.md:137
msgid ""
"If the new version requires config migrations, the startup log emits a "
"warning and the binary usually auto-migrates. Check `zeroclaw config list` "
"to spot-check values after upgrade, and `zeroclaw config migrate` to apply "
"any pending schema migrations manually."
msgstr "如果新版本需要配置迁移，启动日志会发出警告，并且二进制文件通常会自动进行迁移。升级后，请检查 `zeroclaw config list` 以抽查配置值，并使用 `zeroclaw config migrate` 手动应用任何待处理的架构迁移。"

