msgstr "沙盒化、可移植、无 FFI"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:129
msgid "Overhead; limited HW access from Wasm"
msgstr "开销；Wasm 对硬件访问受限"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:130
msgid "**Dynamic linking**"
msgstr "**动态链接**"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:130
msgid "Native speed, full HW access"
msgstr "原生速度，完全硬件访问"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:130
msgid "Platform-specific; security concerns"
msgstr "特定于平台的；安全注意事项"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:131
msgid "**Interpreted DSL**"
msgstr "**解释型 DSL**"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:131
msgid "Safe, auditable"
msgstr "安全、可审计"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:131
msgid "Slower; limited expressiveness"
msgstr "较慢；表达能力有限"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:132
