msgid ""
"**Out of memory** — Keep features minimal (`--features hardware` for Uno Q); "
"consider `compact_context = true`."
msgstr "**内存不足** — 保持功能精简（对于 Uno Q 使用 `--features hardware`）；考虑设置 `compact_context = true`。"

