"\"ok\":true,\"result\":\"done\"}`."
msgstr "协议：换行分隔的 JSON。请求：`{\"id\":\"1\",\"cmd\":\"gpio_write\",\"args\":{\"pin\":13,\"value\":1}}`。响应：`{\"id\":\"1\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":\"done\"}`。"

