msgstr "本文档描述了外部事件如何触发 SOP 运行。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:7
msgid "[MQTT Integration](#2-mqtt-integration)"
msgstr "[MQTT 集成](#2-mqtt-integration)"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:8
msgid "[Webhook Integration](#3-webhook-integration)"
msgstr "[Webhook 集成](#3-webhook-integration)"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:9
msgid "[Cron Integration](#4-cron-integration)"
msgstr "[Cron 集成](#4-cron-integration)"

