msgstr "[故障排除](#6-troubleshooting)"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:13
msgid "1. Overview"
msgstr "1. 概述"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:15
msgid ""
"ZeroClaw routes MQTT/webhook/cron/peripheral events through a unified SOP "
"dispatcher (`dispatch_sop_event`)."
msgstr "ZeroClaw 通过统一的 SOP 调度器（`dispatch_sop_event`）路由 MQTT/webhook/cron/外围设备事件。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:17
msgid "Key behaviors:"
msgstr "关键行为："

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:19
msgid ""
"**Consistent trigger matching:** one matcher path for all event sources."
msgstr "**一致的触发器匹配：** 所有事件源使用一个匹配器路径。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:20
msgid "**Run-start audit:** started runs are persisted via `SopAuditLogger`."
msgstr "**运行开始审计：** 已启动的运行通过 `SopAuditLogger` 进行持久化。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:21
msgid ""
"**Headless safety:** in non-agent-loop contexts, `ExecuteStep` actions are "
"logged as pending (not silently executed)."
msgstr "**无头模式安全性：** 在非智能体循环上下文中，`ExecuteStep` 操作会被记录为待处理状态（而非静默执行）。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:23
msgid "2. MQTT Integration"
msgstr "2. MQTT 集成"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:25
msgid "2.1 Configuration"
msgstr "2.1 配置"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:27
msgid ""
"Configure broker access with `zeroclaw config set channels.mqtt.<field> "
"<value>` — the keys land under `[channels.mqtt]` in the stored config. See "
"the [Config reference](../reference/config.md) for all fields. The `use_tls` "
"flag must match the scheme of `broker_url` (`mqtts://` ⇒ `true`, `mqtt://` ⇒ "
"`false`)."
msgstr "使用 `zeroclaw config set channels.mqtt.<field> <value>` 配置代理访问权限——这些键会存储在配置文件的 `[channels.mqtt]` 部分。有关所有字段的详细信息，请参阅 [配置参考](../reference/config.md)。`use_tls` 标志必须与 `broker_url` 的方案匹配（`mqtts://` ⇒ `true`，`mqtt://` ⇒ `false`）。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:29
msgid "2.2 Trigger Definition"
msgstr "2.2 触发器定义"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:31
msgid "In `SOP.toml`:"
msgstr "在 `SOP.toml` 中："

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:33
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[[triggers]]\n"
"type = \"mqtt\"\n"
"topic = \"sensors/alert\"\n"
"condition = \"$.severity >= 2\"\n"
"```"
msgstr "```toml\n[[triggers]]\ntype = \"mqtt\"\ntopic = \"sensors/alert\"\ncondition = \"$.severity >= 2\"\n```"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:40
msgid ""
"MQTT payload is forwarded into SOP event payload (`event.payload`), then "
"shown in step context."
msgstr "MQTT 负载被转发到 SOP 事件负载（`event.payload`），然后在步骤上下文中显示。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:42
msgid "3. Webhook Integration"
msgstr "3. Webhook 集成"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:44
msgid "3.1 Endpoints"
msgstr "3.1 端点"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:46
msgid ""
"**`POST /sop/{*rest}`**: SOP-only endpoint. Returns `404` if no SOP matches. "
"No LLM fallback."
msgstr "**`POST /sop/{*rest}`**：仅 SOP 端点。如果没有匹配的 SOP，则返回 `404`。无 LLM 回退。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:47
msgid ""
"**`POST /webhook`**: chat endpoint. It attempts SOP dispatch first; if no "
"match, falls back to normal LLM flow."
msgstr "**`POST /webhook`**：聊天端点。它首先尝试 SOP 分发；如果没有匹配，则回退到正常的 LLM 流程。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:49
msgid "Path matching is exact against configured webhook trigger path."
msgstr "路径匹配与配置的 Webhook 触发器路径完全一致。"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:53
msgid "Trigger path in SOP: `path = \"/sop/deploy\"`"
msgstr "SOP 中的触发路径：`path = \"/sop/deploy\"`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:54
msgid "Matching request: `POST /sop/deploy`"
msgstr "匹配请求：`POST /sop/deploy`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:56
msgid "3.2 Authorization"
msgstr "3.2 授权"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:58
msgid "When pairing is enabled (default), provide:"
msgstr "当启用配对（默认）时，请提供："

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:60
msgid "`Authorization: Bearer <token>` (from `POST /pair`)"
msgstr "`Authorization: Bearer <token>`（来自 `POST /pair`）"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:61
msgid ""
"Optional second layer: `X-Webhook-Secret: <secret>` when webhook secret is "
"configured"
msgstr "可选的第二层：当配置了 webhook 密钥时，使用 `X-Webhook-Secret: <secret>`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:63
msgid "3.3 Idempotency"
msgstr "3.3 幂等性"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:67
msgid "`X-Idempotency-Key: <unique-key>`"
msgstr "`X-Idempotency-Key: <唯一键>`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:69
msgid "Defaults:"
msgstr "默认值："

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:71
msgid "TTL: 300s"
msgstr "TTL：300秒"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:72
msgid "Duplicate response: `200 OK` with `\"status\": \"duplicate\"`"
msgstr "重复响应：`200 OK`，其中 `\"status\": \"duplicate\"`"

#: src/sop/connectivity.md:74
msgid "Idempotency keys are namespaced per endpoint (`/webhook` vs `/sop/*`)."
msgstr "幂等键按端点命名空间隔离（`/webhook` 与 `/sop/*`）。"

