#: src/foundations/fnd-002-documentation-standards.md:694
msgid ""
"Write `docs/architecture/diagrams/component-map.md` (Mermaid, reflects "
"target crate topology)"
msgstr "```markdown\n# 组件映射图\n\n本文件描述了目标 crate 的拓扑结构。\n\n## 架构图\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    A[crate_a] --> B[crate_b]\n    A --> C[crate_c]\n    B --> D[crate_d]\n    C --> D\n```\n\n## 说明\n\n- `crate_a` 是核心 crate，依赖于 `crate_b` 和 `crate_c`。\n- `crate_b` 和 `crate_c` 都依赖于 `crate_d`。\n```"

#: src/foundations/fnd-002-documentation-standards.md:695
msgid ""
"Write `docs/architecture/diagrams/data-flow.md` (Mermaid, message lifecycle)"
msgstr "```markdown\n# 数据流\n\n本文档描述了消息在系统中的生命周期。\n\n## 消息生命周期\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User\n    participant API\n    participant Queue\n    participant Worker\n    participant Database\n\n    User->>API: 发送消息\n    API->>Queue: 将消息入队\n    Queue->>Worker: 传递消息\n    Worker->>Database: 存储消息\n    Worker->>User: 返回确认\n```\n\n### 步骤说明\n\n1. **用户发送消息**：用户通过 API 发送消息。\n2. **API 接收消息**：API 接收消息并将其放入消息队列。\n3. **消息入队**：消息被添加到消息队列中等待处理。\n4. **Worker 处理消息**：Worker 从队列中取出消息并进行处理。\n5. **存储消息**：处理后的消息被存储到数据库中。\n6. **返回确认**：Worker 向用户返回处理完成的确认信息。\n```"

