"ADR format used in Section 6."
msgstr "**Michael Nygard 关于 ADR 的文章** — https://cognitect.com/blog/2011/11/15/documenting-architecture-decisions — 这篇原始文章介绍了在第 6 节中使用的 ADR 格式。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-002-documentation-standards.md:751
