#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:737
msgid "8. The RFC Governance Loop"
msgstr "8. RFC 治理循环"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:739
msgid ""
"The RFC process was established in the documentation RFC and the "
"architecture RFC. This section defines the close loop — how an RFC moves "
"from proposal to decision to action."
msgstr "RFC 流程在文档 RFC 和架构 RFC 中确立。本节定义了闭环——即 RFC 如何从提案到决策再到行动。"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:741
msgid "8.1 The Full RFC Lifecycle"
msgstr "8.1 RFC 的完整生命周期"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:787
