msgstr "诚实评估：代码库在告诉我们什么"

#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:67
#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:140
msgid "2.1 The Evidence"
msgstr "2.1 证据"

#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:68
#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:170
msgid "2.2 What the Numbers Do Not Show"
msgstr "2.2 数字未显示的内容"

#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:69
#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:188
msgid "2.3 What Is Already Good"
msgstr "2.3 已经做得好的部分"

#: src/foundations/fnd-006-zero-compromise-in-practice.md:70
