msgstr "所有第三方操作引用必须固定到完整的提交 SHA（根据上述白名单策略）。"

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:137
msgid ""
"Keep `ci.yml`, `dev/ci.sh`, and `.githooks/pre-push` aligned — the same "
"quality gates run locally and in CI."
msgstr "保持 `ci.yml`、`dev/ci.sh` 和 `.githooks/pre-push` 同步——确保本地和 CI 中运行相同的质量检查。"

#: src/maintainers/ci-and-actions.md:138
msgid ""
"`docs-quality` checks are not in the required gate. Run them locally with "
"`bash scripts/ci/docs_quality_gate.sh`."
msgstr "`docs-quality` 检查未包含在必需的门禁中。请通过运行 `bash scripts/ci/docs_quality_gate.sh` 在本地执行这些检查。"

