msgstr "在 GitHub Release 最终确定之前，即可匹配 GHCR 镜像标签（`ghcr.io/<owner>/<repo>:<tag>`）。"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:40
msgid "All artifact files exist before the Release is published."
msgstr "所有工件文件在发布之前均已存在。"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:42
msgid ""
"If any of these fail, the run halts mid-pipeline and reports the specific "
"gate."
msgstr "如果其中任何一项失败，运行将在管道中途停止，并报告具体的门控。"

