#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:167
msgid "Operational principles"
msgstr "操作原理"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:169
msgid "Keep release changes small and reversible."
msgstr "保持发布变更小巧且可逆。"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:170
msgid ""
"One release issue/checklist per version so handoff between maintainers is "
"clean."
msgstr "每个版本对应一个发布问题/清单，以便维护者之间的交接清晰明了。"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:171
msgid "Never publish from an ad-hoc feature branch."
msgstr "切勿从临时功能分支发布。"

#: src/maintainers/release-runbook.md:172
msgid ""
"Don't extend the release pipeline mid-cycle. Pipeline changes go through "
"their own review and ship in their own release."
msgstr "不要在发布周期中扩展发布流水线。流水线变更需经过其自身的审查，并在其各自的发布中上线。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:1
msgid "Changelog Generation"
msgstr "生成变更日志"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:3
msgid ""
"The authoritative procedure for assembling `CHANGELOG-next.md` between "
"stable releases. This page is loaded by the `changelog-generation` skill and "
"read by maintainers running a release manually — both consume the same "
"protocol."
msgstr "在稳定版本之间，用于组装 `CHANGELOG-next.md` 的权威流程。此页面由 `changelog-generation` 技能加载，并由手动执行发布的维护者读取——两者均使用相同的协议。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:5
msgid ""
"The release workflows (`release-stable-manual.yml`) automatically use "
"`CHANGELOG-next.md` as the GitHub Release body if it's at the repo root when "
"a release fires. After the stable release ships, the workflow deletes the "
"file. No manual cleanup needed."
msgstr "发布工作流（`release-stable-manual.yml`）在触发发布时，如果 `CHANGELOG-next.md` 文件位于仓库根目录，则会自动将其用作 GitHub Release 的正文内容。稳定版发布完成后，工作流会删除该文件，无需手动清理。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:7
msgid "1. Establish the commit range"
msgstr "1. 确定提交范围"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:9
msgid "Default: last stable tag → HEAD"
msgstr "默认：最后一个稳定标签 → HEAD"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:12
msgid "$(git tag --sort=-creatordate | grep -vE '\\-beta\\.' | head -1)"
msgstr "$(git tag --sort=-creatordate | grep -vE '\\-beta\\.' | head -1)"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:13
msgid "\"Range: ${PREV_TAG}..HEAD\""
msgstr "范围：${PREV_TAG}..HEAD"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:16
msgid "User-specified range"
msgstr "用户指定的范围"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:18
msgid "Accept any of the following and normalize to `<from>..<to>`:"
msgstr "接受以下任意格式，并规范化为 `<from>..<to>`："

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:20
msgid "Input"
msgstr "输入"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:20
msgid "Interpretation"
msgstr "解释"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:22
msgid "`v0.7.2`"
msgstr "`v0.7.2`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:22
msgid "`v0.7.2..HEAD`"
msgstr "`v0.7.2..HEAD`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:23
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:24
msgid "`v0.7.1..v0.7.2`"
msgstr "`v0.7.1..v0.7.2`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:23
msgid "Exactly as given"
msgstr "Exactly as given"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:24
msgid "`v0.7.1 v0.7.2`"
msgstr "`v0.7.1 v0.7.2`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:26
msgid "Verify both refs exist before proceeding:"
msgstr "在继续之前，请验证两个引用（refs）是否存在："

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:29
msgid "\"ERROR: ref not found\""
msgstr "错误：未找到引用"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:32
msgid "2. Collect and categorise commits"
msgstr "2. 收集并分类提交"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:34
msgid "Collect"
msgstr "收集"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:37
msgid "\"%H %h %s\""
msgstr "\"%H %h %s\""

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:40
msgid "Save full SHAs for the contributor resolution step:"
msgstr "在贡献者解析步骤中保存完整的 SHA："

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:43
msgid "\"%H\""
msgstr "\"%H\""

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:46
msgid "Categorise"
msgstr "分类"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:48
msgid ""
"Map each commit to a section by its conventional commit prefix. Commits "
"without a recognized prefix must still be read and categorized by content — "
"never silently drop them."
msgstr "根据约定式提交前缀将每个提交映射到对应的章节。没有识别到前缀的提交仍需阅读并按内容分类——切勿静默丢弃。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:52
msgid "`feat:`, `feat(*)`"
msgstr "`feat:`，`feat(*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:52
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:65
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:144
msgid "What's New"
msgstr "更新内容"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:53
msgid "`fix:`, `fix(*)`"
msgstr "`fix:`，`fix(*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:53
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:66
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:165
msgid "Bug Fixes"
msgstr "错误修复"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:54
msgid "`refactor:`, `perf:`"
msgstr "`重构：`, `性能：`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:54
msgid "What's New (group as \"Improvements\")"
msgstr "新增功能（归类为“改进”）"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:55
msgid "`security:`, `fix(*security*)`"
msgstr "`security:`，`fix(*security*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:55
msgid "What's New → Security"
msgstr "新增功能 → 安全性"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:56
msgid "`docs:`, `docs(*)`"
msgstr "`docs:`，`docs(*)`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:56
msgid "What's New → Documentation (omit trivial typo fixes)"
msgstr "更新内容 → 文档（省略琐碎的拼写错误修复）"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:57
msgid "`chore:`, `ci:`, `build:`"
msgstr "`chore:`、`ci:`、`build:`"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:57
msgid "Omit unless user-visible (new install path, dropped platform, etc.)"
msgstr "除非用户可见（例如新的安装路径、已移除的平台等），否则省略。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:58
msgid "`breaking:` or `!` suffix"
msgstr "`breaking:` 或 `!` 后缀"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:58
msgid "Breaking Changes — always surface"
msgstr "破坏性变更 — 始终显示"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:59
msgid "No prefix"
msgstr "无前缀"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:59
msgid "Read body; categorize by content; note in review"
msgstr "读取正文；按内容分类；在审查中注明"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:61
msgid "Section ordering in the output file"
msgstr "输出文件中的章节顺序"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:63
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:136
msgid "Preamble"
msgstr "前言"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:64
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:140
msgid "Highlights"
msgstr "亮点"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:67
msgid "Breaking Changes (omit if empty)"
msgstr "破坏性变更（若为空则省略）"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:68
#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:180
msgid "Contributors"
msgstr "贡献者"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:70
msgid "3. Contributor resolution"
msgstr "3. 贡献者解析"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:72
msgid ""
"Do **not** use `git log --pretty=format:\"%an\"` alone — it misses everyone "
"listed in `Co-Authored-By` trailers. Use the GitHub GraphQL `authors` field, "
"which resolves direct authors and co-authors."
msgstr "不要单独使用 `git log --pretty=format:\"%an\"` —— 它会遗漏 `Co-Authored-By` 尾注中列出的所有贡献者。请使用 GitHub GraphQL 的 `authors` 字段，该字段可以解析直接作者和共同作者。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:74
msgid "Query"
msgstr "查询"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:76
msgid ""
"Paginate in batches of 100 commits. Use `pageInfo.endCursor` while "
"`hasNextPage` is `true`."
msgstr "每批分页 100 个提交。当 `hasNextPage` 为 `true` 时，使用 `pageInfo.endCursor`。"

#: src/maintainers/changelog-generation.md:78
msgid ""
"```graphql\n"
"{\n"
"  repository(owner: \"zeroclaw-labs\", name: \"zeroclaw\") {\n"
"    ref(qualifiedName: \"refs/heads/master\") {\n"
"      target {\n"
"        ... on Commit {\n"
"          history(first: 100) {\n"
"            pageInfo { hasNextPage endCursor }\n"
"            nodes {\n"
"              oid\n"
"              authors(first: 10) {\n"
"                nodes {\n"
"                  user { login }\n"
"                  email\n"
"                }\n"
"              }\n"
"            }\n"
"          }\n"
"        }\n"
"      }\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr "```graphql\n{\n  repository(owner: \"zeroclaw-labs\", name: \"zeroclaw\") {\n    ref(qualifiedName: \"refs/heads/master\") {\n      target {\n        ... on Commit {\n          history(first: 100) {\n            pageInfo { hasNextPage endCursor }\n            nodes {\n              oid\n              authors(first: 10) {\n                nodes {\n                  user { login }\n                  email\n                }\n              }\n            }\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```"

